NK105(be)002:18605: u pa ya ste spyod pa dang /
NK105(be)002:18607: tan+d+ra ste rgyud du grags pa de gsum ni thub
NK105(be)002:18608: pas gsungs pa phyi mtshan nyid kyi theg pa ltar
NK105(be)002:18609: gtsang sbra dang sdom pa'i kun spyod kyi tshul mtshungs
NK105(be)002:18610: pas thub pa rgyud kyi theg pa zhes bya'o //
NK105(be)002:18611: de dag gsang sngags phyi bar bzhag tshul ni /
NK105(be)002:18613: de dag gsang sngags phyi ste lha rnams kyang //
NK105(be)002:18614: yab yum zung 'brel bsgom par mi nus shing //
NK105(be)002:18615: sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga sogs bsten mi byed //
NK105(be)002:18616: gtsang sbra kun du spyod pas gnas pa yin //
NK105(be)002:18617: de'ang bya ba dang spyod pa'i rgyud ni sems dpa' dang sems ma /
NK105(be)002:18618: rig sngags dang gzungs sngags kyi lha de dag rje
NK105(be)002:18619: khol dang spun grogs kyi tshul du bzhugs kyi zung
NK105(be)002:18621: rnal 'byor gyi rgyud du dkyil 'khor gyi gru chad
NK105(be)002:18622: la bkod pa chen po longs spyod rdzogs pa ltar
NK105(be)002:18623: bstan gyi zung 'brel du ma yin zhing /
NK105(be)002:18624: thabs dang shes rab rim can du bsgom pas bskyed rdzogs so so ba nyid dang /
NK105(be)002:18625: dam rdzas sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga la sogs pa bsten par mi byed /
NK105(be)002:18626: de dag la btsog pa'i gnas su 'dzin pas gtsang sbra kun du spyod pas gnas pa'i phyir te /
NK105(be)002:18627: dbang chen rol ba'i rgyud las /
NK105(be)002:18628: thabs dang shes rab dgyes sprin ye shes grub pa'i dngos //
NK105(be)002:18629: sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga dang bde chen mchog rol pa //
NK105(be)002:18630: rmad byung la yin tshul 'di de las gzhan gyur cing //
NK105(be)002:18631: gtsang sbras gdung rnams skal ba dman pas de lta min //
NK105(be)002:18633: nang rgyud sde gsum gyi dbye ba ni /
NK105(be)002:18634: sngags nang pa gsum gyi dbye ba ni /
NK105(be)002:18635: rnal 'byor bla med rgyud la'ang gsum yin te //
NK105(be)002:18636: pha ma gnyis su med pa bla na med //
NK105(be)002:18637: bskyed rdzogs gnyis med gtso bor ston pa ste //
NK105(be)002:18638: ma h+aa a nu a ti zhes bya'o //
NK105(be)002:18639: lha yang 'khril sbyor dam rdzas khyad par can //
NK105(be)002:18640: gtsang btsog gnyis med thams cad ro gcig tu //
NK105(be)002:18641: dkyil 'khor gcig gi rol par ston pa yin //
NK105(be)002:18642: de la dpal gsang ba 'dus pa dang /
NK105(be)002:18643: 'jam dpal gshin rje'i gshed la sogs pa rnal 'byor
NK105(be)002:18644: pa'i rgyud rnams ni ma h+aa yo ga ste bskyed
NK105(be)002:18646: de'i rdzogs rim yang rlung gtso bor ston pa yin la /
NK105(be)002:18650: kye rdo rje la sogs pa ni shes rab ma'i rgyud de a nu yo ga zhes bya ste /
NK105(be)002:18651: shes rab rdzogs pa'i rim pa gtso bor ston zhing /
NK105(be)002:18652: rdzogs rim yang khams byang chub kyi sems thig le
NK105(be)002:18653: gtso bor byed pas bde stong rnam par mi rtog
NK105(be)002:18655: gnyis su med pa'i rgyud sgyu 'phrul dra ba chen
NK105(be)002:18656: po la sogs pa ni a ti yo ga zhes
NK105(be)002:18657: bya ste / thabs shes rab 'du 'bral med pa'i
NK105(be)002:18658: ngo bo bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug gtso bor ston zhing
NK105(be)002:18659: bya ste / / rdzogs rim yang rtsa rlung thig le las skyes pa'i bde ba /
NK105(be)002:18662: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i 'od gsal ye shes chen
NK105(be)002:18663: po zhes bya ba gtso bor 'dod pa yin no
NK105(be)002:18664: // de gsum ka'ang re re zhing thabs shes zung
NK105(be)002:18665: 'jug tu 'brel pa'i brdar yab yum 'khril sbyor du
NK105(be)002:18666: // bskyed pa dang / spang blang dang /
NK105(be)002:18668: gtsang btsog la sogs pa bzang ngan blang dor med
NK105(be)002:18669: pa'i don gyi phyir sha dang chang la sogs pa'i
NK105(be)002:18671: chos thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i dkyil 'khor gcig tu 'tshang rgya bar 'dod de /
NK105(be)002:18672: dpal gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges
NK105(be)002:18673: pa'i rgyud kyi rgyal po sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba chen
NK105(be)002:18674: po las / chos thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas
NK105(be)002:18675: pa'i ngo bo nyid du gcig pa'i mtshan nyid yin
NK105(be)002:18677: de dag so so'i 'dod tshul ni /
NK105(be)002:18678: rgyud sde de dag gi 'dod tshul la /
NK105(be)002:18679: bya bas rang nyid dman la lha nyid mchog /
NK105(be)002:18680: rje khol tshul du bsgrub pas dngos grub len //
NK105(be)002:18681: spyod pas rang dang lha gnyis mnyam par blta //
NK105(be)002:18682: rang nyid dam tshig mdun du ye shes lha //
NK105(be)002:18683: grogs pa'i tshul gyis dngos grub len pa yin //
NK105(be)002:18684: rnal 'byor dngos gzhir gnyis su med pa la //
NK105(be)002:18685: sbyor rjes lha ni dgug gshegs gnyis su byed //
NK105(be)002:18686: chu la chu bzhag gnyis med dngos grub len //
NK105(be)002:18687: de la bya ba'i rgyud ni /
NK105(be)002:18688: lha ye shes pa rgyal po ltar byas te /
NK105(be)002:18689: rang nyid dmangs kyi tshul gyis dngos grub len par 'dod de /
NK105(be)002:18690: rigs thams cad pa'i dngos grub len pa'i rgyud las /
NK105(be)002:18691: rje dpon rgyal po'i skur bltas la //
NK105(be)002:18692: rang nyid bran gyi 'du shes kyis //
NK105(be)002:18693: sngags sgrub dngos grub snying po ni //
NK105(be)002:18694: bla na med pa'i mchog tu blang //
NK105(be)002:18697: rang nyid dam tshig sems dpar bskyed pa'i mdun du /
NK105(be)002:18698: lha ye shes sems dpa' spun nam grogs po'i tshul du mdun du bskyed nas dngos grub len te /
NK105(be)002:18700: spun nam grogs kyi tshul tsam du //
NK105(be)002:18701: dngos grub dam pa blang bar bya //
NK105(be)002:18704: bdag lha'i rnal 'byor du bsgoms te /
NK105(be)002:18705: sbyor ba ye shes pa dgug cing bstim pa dang /
NK105(be)002:18706: phyag rgya bzhis rgyas gdab pa la sogs pa byas
NK105(be)002:18707: nas mchod bstod bzlas pa la sogs byas pa'i mthar
NK105(be)002:18708: yang gshegs su gsol ba yin la /
NK105(be)002:18709: dngos gzhi gnyis su med pa'i dus der dngos grub 'dod pa yin te /
NK105(be)002:18711: gnyis su med pa'i chos dbyings dang //
NK105(be)002:18712: bla med dngos grub dam pa blang //
NK105(be)002:18714: de'ang de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs dang /
NK105(be)002:18716: rdo rje'i rigs gsum spyi'i sngags dang phyag rgyas byin gyis rlob cing /
NK105(be)002:18720: phyag rgya chen po bzhis rgyas 'debs pa yin no //
NK105(be)002:18721: gong ma gsum gtso bor byed tshul ni /
NK105(be)002:18722: rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud la ni /
NK105(be)002:18723: ma h+aas rlung dang bskyed rim thabs gtso la //
NK105(be)002:18724: a nus khams dang rdzogs rim shes rab gtso //
NK105(be)002:18725: a tis thams cad gnyis med ye shes gtso //
NK105(be)002:18726: kun kyang chos kun ye nas mnyam pa nyid //
NK105(be)002:18727: yin par shes pa'i tshul gyis nyams su len //
NK105(be)002:18728: de la chos thams cad ye nas ma skyes pa
NK105(be)002:18729: stong pa nyid du gnas pas sems nyid nam mkha'
NK105(be)002:18730: lta bur bdag med par shes te nyams su len
NK105(be)002:18731: pa ni / gsang ba 'dus pa las /
NK105(be)002:18732: dngos po 'di rnams ma skyes pas //
NK105(be)002:18733: chos dang chos nyid med pa ste //
NK105(be)002:18734: nam mkha' lta bar bdag med pa //
NK105(be)002:18736: zhes 'gyur snga ma las bshad do //
NK105(be)002:18739: dngos po thams cad dang bral ba'i //
NK105(be)002:18740: phung po khams dang skye mched dang //
NK105(be)002:18741: gzung dang 'dzin pa rnam par spangs //
NK105(be)002:18742: chos bdag med pa mnyam nyid pas //
NK105(be)002:18743: rang sems gdod nas ma skyes pa //
NK105(be)002:18744: stong pa nyid kyi rang bzhin no //
NK105(be)002:18746: de ltar shes nas thabs pha'i rgyud rnams dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'i rim pa thabs dang /
NK105(be)002:18747: 'byung ba lnga'i rlung rnam par dag pa gsal stong
NK105(be)002:18748: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes gtso bor byed
NK105(be)002:18749: pas mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub sgrub par
NK105(be)002:18750: byed do // shes rab ma'i rgyud las ni bskyed
NK105(be)002:18751: rim gyi spros pa shas chung bas khams bde ba
NK105(be)002:18752: chen po yi ge b+ha ga'i dkyil 'khor las mkha'
NK105(be)002:18753: gsang byang chub mchog gi rim pas gzhan lus phyag
NK105(be)002:18754: rgya dang rang lus thabs ldan la brten nas dga'
NK105(be)002:18755: ba bzhi'i ye shes bde ba chen pos byang chub
NK105(be)002:18757: gnyis su med pa'i rgyud sde las ni de gnyis
NK105(be)002:18758: ka'i rim pa las khyad par du ye shes chen
NK105(be)002:18759: po gcig dang du ma med pa'i chos nyid 'od
NK105(be)002:18760: gsal ba gtso bor byed pas byang chub sgrub par
NK105(be)002:18761: byed do // 'od gsal ba de yang gsum ste /
NK105(be)002:18765: dang po khams las su rung ba las ting nge 'dzin skye /
NK105(be)002:18766: de las mchog mi 'gyur gyi bde ba nam mkha'i
NK105(be)002:18767: dbyings khyab par zag pa med pa'i bde bas gang
NK105(be)002:18768: ba skye'o // de ni dbu mar dngas ma chen po bab pa las byung ba'o //
NK105(be)002:18769: gsal ba la yang gnyis las /
NK105(be)002:18770: nang du rlung lnga stobs su gyur pas dngas gsal
NK105(be)002:18771: g.yo ba med pa'i ye shes bsam gtan bzhi'i rim
NK105(be)002:18773: phyir ye shes lnga'i 'od lnga sku dang thig le
NK105(be)002:18774: dang 'od snang du snang bas nam mkha' khyab par
NK105(be)002:18775: gnas te / 'jal dpal sgyu 'phrul dra ba las /
NK105(be)002:18776: ye shes snang ba lam me ba //
NK105(be)002:18777: 'gro ba'i mar me ye shes sgron //
NK105(be)002:18778: gzi brjid chen po 'od gsal ba //
NK105(be)002:18780: gzi brjid phreng ldan lta na sdug /'od bzang 'bar ba dpal gyi be'u //
NK105(be)002:18782: de'ang rlung lnga'i dngas ma dbu mar chud pa na /
NK105(be)002:18783: sa'i rlung gi dngas ma dbu mar chud pas nang du sems gnas pa dang /
NK105(be)002:18784: phyir 'od ser po rin chen 'byung gnas gsal bas mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes la spyod /
NK105(be)002:18786: zad par sa'i ting nge 'dzin la dbang bsgyur /
NK105(be)002:18787: rin po che brtsegs pa'i 'jig rten bgrod pa'o //
NK105(be)002:18788: chu'i rlung gi dngas ma dbu mar chud pas nang du dngas la rnyog pa med pa'i sems gsal /
NK105(be)002:18789: phyir 'od dkar po mi bskyod par gsal bas me long lta bu'i ye shes la spyod /
NK105(be)002:18791: zad par chu'i ting nge 'dzin la dbang bsgyur /
NK105(be)002:18792: mngon par dga' ba'i 'jig rten bgrod pa'o //
NK105(be)002:18793: me'i dngas ma'i rlung dbu mar chud pas nang du bde drod skye /
NK105(be)002:18794: phyir 'od dmar po snang ba mtha' yas gsal bas so sor rtog pa'i ye shes la spyod /
NK105(be)002:18796: zad par me'i ting nge 'dzin la dbang bsgyur /
NK105(be)002:18797: bde ba can gyi 'jig rten bgrod pa'o //
NK105(be)002:18798: rlung gi dngas ma'i rlung dbu mar chud pas nang du sems g.yo ba dang mched pa 'thob /
NK105(be)002:18799: phyir 'od ljang gu don yod grub par gsal bas bya ba grub pa'i ye shes la spyod /
NK105(be)002:18801: zad par rlung gi ting nge 'dzin la dbang bsgyur /
NK105(be)002:18802: las rab grub pa'i 'jig rten bgrod pa'o //
NK105(be)002:18803: nam mkha'i rlung ni de thams cad pa'i chos nyid de shin tu dngas la mi rtog pas /
NK105(be)002:18804: de'i dngas ma dbu mar chud pas nang du rnam par mi rtog pa dang /
NK105(be)002:18805: phyir 'od mthing ga rnam par snang mdzad gsal bas chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes la spyod /
NK105(be)002:18807: zad par nam mkha'i khams la dbang bsgyur /
NK105(be)002:18808: 'og min stug po bkod pa'am mkha' spyod kyi zhing bgrod pa yin te /
NK105(be)002:18809: sgyu 'phrul dra ba chen po las /
NK105(be)002:18810: de ltar rnal 'byor skal chen po //
NK105(be)002:18811: rlung lnga'i dngas ma stobs gyur pas //
NK105(be)002:18812: 'od lnga nang gi ye shes lnga //
NK105(be)002:18813: sku lnga bgrod pa'i zhing khams lnga //
NK105(be)002:18814: zad par lnga stsogs thob par 'gyur //
NK105(be)002:18816: chos thams cad dkyil 'khor gyi rang bzhin du bsgom tshul ni /
NK105(be)002:18817: da ni chos thams cad dkyil 'khor gsum gyi rang
NK105(be)002:18818: bzhin du mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa'i tshul
NK105(be)002:18820: bdag dang 'gro kun ye nas sangs rgyas pas //
NK105(be)002:18821: phung po khams dang skye mched la sogs kun //
NK105(be)002:18822: dkyil 'khor gcig tu gsal btab rim gnyis bsgom //
NK105(be)002:18823: de la 'dir chos thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas
NK105(be)002:18824: pa'i dkyil 'khor gsum gyi rang bzhin du shes par
NK105(be)002:18826: gzhi rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor du lta bas thag bcad pa /
NK105(be)002:18827: lam ting nge 'dzin zab mo'i dkyil 'khor du sgom pas nyams su blang ba /
NK105(be)002:18828: 'bras bu byang chub mchog gi dkyil 'khor du don gnyis phun sum tshogs par bstan pa'o //
NK105(be)002:18830: dag pa gzhi'i gnas lugs dang /
NK105(be)002:18831: ma dag pa gzhi'i 'khrul tshul lo //
NK105(be)002:18833: gdod ma'i sems nyid stong pa chos sku'i snying po /
NK105(be)002:18834: gsal ba longs sku'i rang bzhin /
NK105(be)002:18838: rin po che ltar 'dod dgu lhun gyis grub pa /
NK105(be)002:18843: 'phrin las lnga ste sangs rgyas kyi yon tan rang chas su ye nas yod pa nyid /
NK105(be)002:18845: stong nyid bdag med ye mkhyen rang rig thugs //
NK105(be)002:18846: dmigs bya dmigs byed med par dran dbang bsgyur //
NK105(be)002:18847: ngo mtshar sku gsung yon tan zhing khams las //
NK105(be)002:18848: gzhan na med de de nyid de ltar yin //
NK105(be)002:18850: byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po las /
NK105(be)002:18851: kye sems dpa' chen po nyon cig /
NK105(be)002:18852: kun byed byang chub nga yi rang bzhin las //
NK105(be)002:18853: ma btsal rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa ni //
NK105(be)002:18854: rgyal ba kun gyi snying po sku gsum ste //
NK105(be)002:18855: nga yi rang bzhin ma bcos chos skur grub //
NK105(be)002:18856: nga yi ngo bo ma bcos longs spyod rdzogs //
NK105(be)002:18857: nga yi thugs rje mngon phyung sprul sku gsum //
NK105(be)002:18858: btsal nas grub pa'i 'bras bu bstan pa min //
NK105(be)002:18859: ma btsal ye nas lhun gyis grub pa yin //
NK105(be)002:18861: de lta bu'i don de khams sam snying po zhes
NK105(be)002:18862: bya ba sngar smos pa nyid de yon tan lhun
NK105(be)002:18863: grub chen por ye nas gnas pa yin no //
NK105(be)002:18864: ma dag pa gzhi'i 'khrul tshul ni /
NK105(be)002:18865: de lta bu'i ngang las sngar smos pa bzhin 'khrul te /
NK105(be)002:18867: e ma'o bde gshegs snying po las //
NK105(be)002:18868: rang gi rnam rtog las kyis 'khrul //
NK105(be)002:18869: sna tshogs lus dang longs spyod dang //
NK105(be)002:18870: gnas dang sdug bsngal la sogs pa //
NK105(be)002:18871: bdag dang bdag gir so sor 'dzin //
NK105(be)002:18873: srid rtsa'i nyes dmigs bdag tu rtog las 'phros //
NK105(be)002:18874: rgyud drug skye 'gag lus dang longs spyod dang //
NK105(be)002:18875: gnas dang sdug bsngal 'khrul 'khor la sogs pa //
NK105(be)002:18876: log rtog nyid las gzhan du ci yang med //
NK105(be)002:18878: de ltar 'gro ba rigs drug so sor 'khor ba las /
NK105(be)002:18879: khyad par du mi rnams 'khrul dus dang po mngal gnas 'dzin pa na /
NK105(be)002:18880: thog mar mig gnyis dang lte ba'i rtsa mdud du chags te /
NK105(be)002:18881: de las lus rnams bskyed pa dang /
NK105(be)002:18882: dngas ma'i dbang por gyur pa las /
NK105(be)002:18883: rtsa gsum ka ba'i tshul du gnas pa'i nang na /
NK105(be)002:18884: +aahmh'u gsum yi ge'i rnam pa can du gsal ba des /
NK105(be)002:18885: phyir lus ngag yid gsum gyi rten byed /
NK105(be)002:18886: nang du 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug gsum gyi rten byed /
NK105(be)002:18887: gsang bar sku gsung thugs kyi rten byed do //
NK105(be)002:18888: de'ang dbu ma'i yar sna tshangs bug mar sna gsang
NK105(be)002:18889: gnas la thug pa'i g.yas ro ma dkar ba dang
NK105(be)002:18890: g.yon rkyang ma dmar ba gnyis dbu ma sngo skya'i
NK105(be)002:18891: g.yas g.yon nas phan tshun lu gu rgyud du mdud
NK105(be)002:18892: pa nyi shu rtsa gcig byas te gnas so //
NK105(be)002:18893: de dag la rtsa'i 'khor lo yang /
NK105(be)002:18894: sku gsung thugs bde ba chen po ltar na gsum du gnas te /
NK105(be)002:18895: lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo rtsa 'dab drug cu rtsa bzhi /
NK105(be)002:18896: mgrin pa longs spyod kyi 'khor lo rtsa 'dab bcu drug /
NK105(be)002:18897: snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo rtsa 'dab brgyad du gnas so //
NK105(be)002:18898: sku bzhi ye shes kyi rim pa dang sbyar na /
NK105(be)002:18899: de'i steng du spyi gtsug bde chen gyi 'khor lo rtsa 'dab sum cu rtsa gnyis yod do //
NK105(be)002:18900: sku lnga lhun grub kyi dbang du byas na /
NK105(be)002:18901: de'i steng du gsang gnas bde skyong gi 'khor lo
NK105(be)002:18902: rtsa 'dab bdun cu rtsa gnyis khams dngas ma 'bab
NK105(be)002:18903: pa'i nus ldan du yod do //
NK105(be)002:18904: 'khor lo drug gi rim pa dang sbyar na /
NK105(be)002:18905: gsang ba ye shes kyi 'khor lo /
NK105(be)002:18906: mgrin pa longs spyod kyi 'khor lo /
NK105(be)002:18907: dbu ma bde ba chen po'i 'khor lo /
NK105(be)002:18908: gtsug tor nam mkha'i khams kyi 'khor lo /
NK105(be)002:18910: lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo ste drug tu yod la /
NK105(be)002:18911: sgyu 'phrul ba ltar na ma dag pa rigs drug gi sa bon drug sbyang gzhir gnas pa la /
NK105(be)002:18912: sbyong byed thub pa drug dang /
NK105(be)002:18913: pha rol tu phyin pa drug gi rang bzhin gyis
NK105(be)002:18914: sbyangs pas ye shes lnga bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i
NK105(be)002:18916: 'khor lo re dang po'i bar re ste bcu gnyis
NK105(be)002:18917: su rlung dag pas sa bcu gnyis rdzogs pa'i mthar
NK105(be)002:18918: bcu gsum pa ye shes chen po'i sa rdzogs par
NK105(be)002:18919: 'dod cing / dus 'khor bas 'khor lo drug dang /
NK105(be)002:18920: bar drug ste bcu gnyis la rlung 'pho ba bcu gnyis dang /
NK105(be)002:18922: thig le mi 'pho ba'i dbang gis yar bzlog dus /
NK105(be)002:18923: gsang ba ye shes kyi 'khor lor log pas sa dang po'i rtags skye /
NK105(be)002:18926: de bzhin du nam mkha'i khams kyi 'khor lo'i bar du sa bcu gnyis bgrod /
NK105(be)002:18929: thig le nam mkha'i khams su phyin pas sangs rgya bar 'dod do //
NK105(be)002:18930: sgyu 'phrul rtsa ba'i rgyud kyi dbang du byas na yang 'khor lo gnyis te /
NK105(be)002:18931: snying ga zhi ba'i 'khor lo dang /
NK105(be)002:18933: 'di dag na rtsa 'dab kyang rags pa lha'i grangs dang mnyam la /
NK105(be)002:18934: phra ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa yod do //
NK105(be)002:18935: de'ang bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis dang lnga bcu rtsa brgyad de brgya phrag gcig go //
NK105(be)002:18937: ro ma brkyang ma kun 'dar ma //
NK105(be)002:18938: 'khor lo so so'i dkyil dag na //
NK105(be)002:18939: ka ba'i tshul du gnas pa la //
NK105(be)002:18941: khams dang rlung ni 'bab pa yi //
NK105(be)002:18942: ye shes rtsa ni stong phrag gcig /
NK105(be)002:18943: bdun cu rtsa gnyis bsgres pa yis //
NK105(be)002:18944: nyi khri chig stong drug brgya'i rlung //
NK105(be)002:18946: gzhan ni bzhi stong brgyad khri'o //
NK105(be)002:18949: nye ba'i rtsa rnams du ma ste //
NK105(be)002:18950: de las lus ni bkang nas gnas //
NK105(be)002:18951: de rnams stong phrag bdun cu gnyis //
NK105(be)002:18952: lus la de nyid lha mo rnams //
NK105(be)002:18955: stong phrag bdun cu rtsa gnyis kyi //
NK105(be)002:18956: rtsa rnams kyi ni rigs bshad do //
NK105(be)002:18958: de'ang nyin zhag phrugs gcig la rlung nyi khri chig stong drug brgya rgyu ba yin la /
NK105(be)002:18959: 'gyu ba chung ba ni kun du rtog pa nyon
NK105(be)002:18960: mongs pa brgyad khri bzhi stong gi rim pa dang
NK105(be)002:18961: grangs mnyam pas de dag gi rta byed cing nyon
NK105(be)002:18962: mongs pa nam rgyu ba na de dang mnyam du
NK105(be)002:18964: rang bzhin du pho rlung gyen rgyu stod na gnas pa dang /
NK105(be)002:18965: mo rlung thur sel smad na gnas pa dang /
NK105(be)002:18966: ma ning gi rlung mnyam gnas par na gnas pa gsum bshad do //
NK105(be)002:18978: 'gro 'dug zag pa 'dor ba dang bcas pa'i bya ba byed do //
NK105(be)002:18979: 'di dag ni thun mong du grags pa ste phyi'i rlung lnga'o //
NK105(be)002:18980: nang gi rlung lnga ni 'byung ba lnga'i rlung lnga ste /
NK105(be)002:18986: byed las ni nang gi phung po khams dang skye mched gnas pa'i rten byed /
NK105(be)002:18987: ma dag pa dug lnga dang dag pa ye shes lnga mched pa'i gzhi byed do //
NK105(be)002:18988: gsang ba'i rlung lnga ni ye shes lnga la grags pas rags par med do //
NK105(be)002:18989: khams dngas ma chen po yang dkar po dang dmar po gnyis te /
NK105(be)002:18990: ro brkyang gnyis nas 'khor lo so so'i rtsa 'dab na gnas so //
NK105(be)002:18991: bud med la ni g.yas g.yon go bzlog pas gnas par bshad do //
NK105(be)002:18992: khyad par du zla ba ro ma nas yar sna spyi gtsug gi ham las 'bab cing /
NK105(be)002:18993: nyi ma brkyang ma'i mar sna gsang gnas kyi a las 'bab pa'o //
NK105(be)002:18994: skyes pa'i brkyang ma dang bud med kyi ro ma'i
NK105(be)002:18995: mar sna mdud par gyur pas khams dkar po dang
NK105(be)002:18996: dmar po mi 'dzag par bshad do //
NK105(be)002:18997: rtsa mdud rnams grol ba las sa dang lam gyi yon tan rdzogs par 'dod de /
NK105(be)002:18998: dbu ma'i mdud pa gnyis gnyis grol dus sa bcu'i sa re re rdzogs shing /
NK105(be)002:18999: de'i yon tan thob pa yang khams dngas ma re
NK105(be)002:19000: dang rlung dngas ma re der chud pa'i mthong snang
NK105(be)002:19001: du 'dod de / dper na rtsa mdud dang po gnyis grol /
NK105(be)002:19002: dngas ma gnyis dbu mar chud /
NK105(be)002:19003: lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo'i rtsa chen bzhi'i mdud
NK105(be)002:19004: pa grol ba las sa dang po'i yon tan 'char
NK105(be)002:19005: ba lta bu'o // 'khor lo bzhi'i mdud pa grol
NK105(be)002:19006: ba las sku bzhi thob cing ye shes bzhi mngon
NK105(be)002:19008: da lta rtsa mdud phal na dngas ma dkar dmar
NK105(be)002:19009: gnyis dpa' bo dang dpa' mo'i tshul du 'khril sbyor
NK105(be)002:19010: du yod do // de ltar rtsa yur ba lta
NK105(be)002:19011: bu la khams chu lta bu de rlung shugs lta
NK105(be)002:19012: bus bskyod nas 'gro 'ong du gnas pa ni rdo
NK105(be)002:19013: rje'i lus te ye shes chen po'i rten du gyur
NK105(be)002:19014: du yod do // pa'o // khyad par du sgyu
NK105(be)002:19015: 'phrul chen po'i lugs la snying khong stong gi dkyil
NK105(be)002:19016: na rtsa'i dngas ma rtsa phran rgyus pa bldad pa
NK105(be)002:19021: gcig yon tan gyi rtsa ste /
NK105(be)002:19022: bi ma la'i gsang thig las /
NK105(be)002:19023: gang la yod pa rnam pa brgyad du shes //
NK105(be)002:19027: snying khong stong gi dkyil na rtsa'i dngas ma rtsa
NK105(be)002:19028: phran rgyus pa bldad pa 'dra ba brgyad yod pa
NK105(be)002:19029: las / gsum chos nyid kyi rtsa /
NK105(be)002:19033: de ltar brgyad du shes par bya'o //
NK105(be)002:19035: de'ang dbus kyi gsum ni sku gsum gyi chos nyid mi 'gyur ba'i rten no //
NK105(be)002:19036: mdun na me long ye shes kyi rtsa las ye shes bzhi'i rten byed pa dang /
NK105(be)002:19037: rgyab dang lho na yon tan gyi rtsa zhing khams
NK105(be)002:19038: dang gzhal yas khang la sogs pa'i snang ba 'char
NK105(be)002:19040: g.yon na dug gsum rang rgyud kyi rtsas khams gsum rang mtshan gyi 'khrul snang bskyed pa'o //
NK105(be)002:19041: de'ang chos nyid kyi rtsa'i sbubs na 'od ser po zlum po'i khrod na /
NK105(be)002:19042: sbyang gzhi'i yi ge su dang tri ste lha min dang byol song gi sa bon dang /
NK105(be)002:19043: sbyong byed sku dang ye shes kyi snying po'o //
NK105(be)002:19044: yi ge'i rang 'od za 'og gi gur khang 'dra'o //
NK105(be)002:19045: ye shes kyi rtsa mthing ga gru bzhi'i sbubs na sbyong byed h+aum dang /
NK105(be)002:19046: sbyang gzhi lha mi'i sa bon a dang n+ri ste /
NK105(be)002:19047: dkar dmar mthing ga'i 'od can no //
NK105(be)002:19048: rang rgyud kyi rtsa zla gam dmar po'i sbubs na /
NK105(be)002:19050: sbyang gzhi dmyal ba dang yi dgas kyi sa bon pre dang du'o //
NK105(be)002:19051: de'ang ma dag pa'i dus na las dang nyon mongs
NK105(be)002:19052: pas byas pa'i bag chags gang yin yi ge drug
NK105(be)002:19054: zhe sdang gis las byas pa'i 'khor khong khro la sogs pa ni du'i steng du sog go //
NK105(be)002:19058: gti mug tri'i steng du sog go //
NK105(be)002:19059: rtogs pa'i dus na ye shes kyi rang rtsal dge
NK105(be)002:19060: ba rnams sku gsung thugs kyi yi ge gsum gyi
NK105(be)002:19062: de'ang sku dang 'brel pa lha bsgom pa la sogs pa rnams /
NK105(be)002:19063: sngags bzlas pa la sogs pa +aah /
NK105(be)002:19064: rnam par mi rtog pa bsgom pa la sogs pa
NK105(be)002:19065: h'u gi steng du bzhag pas sbyang gzhi'i yi ge
NK105(be)002:19066: dang de'i steng gi bag chags thams cad dag par
NK105(be)002:19069: gang la ci 'dra de nyid bsres pa bzhin //
NK105(be)002:19070: zhes bya ba chos nyid kyi rtsa la 'od ser po zhig gnas /
NK105(be)002:19072: tshul dngul chu bzhun ma la zhun mar gyi zol yod pa dang 'dra'o //
NK105(be)002:19074: sa bon ni su dang tri /
NK105(be)002:19075: de gsum gyi kha dog ni za 'og gi gur phub pa 'dra'o //
NK105(be)002:19076: ye shes kyi rtsa la 'od mthing ga zhig gnas so //
NK105(be)002:19078: zhags pa thogs pa'am sbrul 'khyil ba 'dra'o //
NK105(be)002:19079: tshul le brgan lce'u la shel gong brgyus pa 'dra'o //
NK105(be)002:19081: sa bon ni a dang n+ri'o //
NK105(be)002:19082: rang rgyud kyi rtsal 'od dmar po zhig gnas so //
NK105(be)002:19083: ci 'dra na dbyibs zla gam dmar po /
NK105(be)002:19084: tshul so ga'i chu la smig rgyu'am /
NK105(be)002:19085: rtsi skya'i kha na zil pa chags pa 'dra /
NK105(be)002:19086: kha dog zangs bzhun ma la ra gan gyi rtsi song ba dang 'dra'o //
NK105(be)002:19088: sa bon ni bre dang du'o //
NK105(be)002:19089: de yang ma rtogs pa'i dus na 'khor ba'i rgyu ste a n+ri la sogs pa'o //
NK105(be)002:19090: rtogs pa'i dus ni ye shes te la sogs pa'o //
NK105(be)002:19091: de gnyis 'dres te byang sems la gnas pa'i tshul
NK105(be)002:19092: gong dang 'dra bas bsres pa bzhin zhes bya'o zhes
NK105(be)002:19093: so // de ltar rtsa tshan pa bzhi la nam shes rnams kyi gnas tshul yang /
NK105(be)002:19095: rnam bzhi bye brag drug las brgyad dkyil na //
NK105(be)002:19096: zhes bya ba chos nyid dang /
NK105(be)002:19099: yon tan gyi rtsa dang bzhi'o //
NK105(be)002:19100: bye brag ni 'od ser po la kun gzhi'i rnam shes gnas so //
NK105(be)002:19101: 'od mthing ga la yid kyi rnam shes gnas so //
NK105(be)002:19102: 'od dmar po la nyon mongs pa can gyi yid gnas so //
NK105(be)002:19103: 'od dmar nag la sgo lnga'i rnam shes gnas so //
NK105(be)002:19104: 'od ser po rtsa'i dngas ma dar dkar gyi skud pa 'dra ba rgyu'o //
NK105(be)002:19105: 'od mthing ga dbugs kyi dngas ma la rgyu'o //
NK105(be)002:19106: 'od dmar po khrag gi dngas ma la rgyu'o //
NK105(be)002:19107: 'od dmar nag sgo lnga'i rtsa'i dngas ma la rgyu'o //
NK105(be)002:19108: 'od ser po'i 'gram na dang su tri gnyis gnas so //
NK105(be)002:19109: 'od mthing ga'i sgab na h'u dang a n+ri gnyis gnas so //
NK105(be)002:19110: 'od dmar po'i sgab na +aahdang pre du gnyis gnas so //
NK105(be)002:19111: 'od dmar nag ni de rnams kyi skyon dang yon tan no //
NK105(be)002:19112: de la a n+ri gnyis dbugs kyi snyigs ma la rgyu'o //
NK105(be)002:19113: su tri gnyis rtsa'i snyigs ma la rgyu'o //
NK105(be)002:19114: pre du gnyis khrag gi snyigs ma la rgyu'o //
NK105(be)002:19115: de yang lha dang mi gnyis su skye ba'i kha
NK105(be)002:19116: zin ni yid kyi rnam par shes pas byas nas
NK105(be)002:19117: sa bon a dang n+ri la sog go //
NK105(be)002:19118: byol song dang lha ma yin du skye ba'i kha
NK105(be)002:19119: zin ni kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pas byas nas
NK105(be)002:19120: sa bon su dang tri la sog go //
NK105(be)002:19121: yi dgas dang dmyal bar skye ba'i kha zin ni
NK105(be)002:19122: sgo lnga'i rnam par shes pa dang nyon mongs pa
NK105(be)002:19123: can gyi yid kyis byas nas sa bon pre dang
NK105(be)002:19125: 'di ltar gnas pa de ni 'gro ba rigs drug
NK105(be)002:19126: gi sems can thams cad la rang rgyud du gnas
NK105(be)002:19127: so zhes so // da ltar snying ga'i rtsa brgyad
NK105(be)002:19128: po'i dbus na rtsa'i dngas ma dar dkar gyi skud
NK105(be)002:19129: pa 'dra ba la sbom phra rta rnga bcur gshags
NK105(be)002:19131: khrag gi dngas ma dang dbugs kyi dngas ma 'dres
NK105(be)002:19132: pa la 'od kha dog lnga ldan shin tu phra
NK105(be)002:19133: ba la sems nyid 'od gsal ba'i chos sku byang
NK105(be)002:19138: snying ga chos kyi pho brang 'og min gyi zhing na /
NK105(be)002:19139: bcom ldan 'das rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas kun du bzang
NK105(be)002:19140: po dus rtag pa rgyun gyi khor mor bzhugs pa
NK105(be)002:19143: lus la ye shes chen po gnas //
NK105(be)002:19144: rtog pa thams cad yang dag spangs //
NK105(be)002:19145: dngos po kun la khyab pa po //
NK105(be)002:19146: lus gnas lus las ma skyes pa'o //
NK105(be)002:19148: de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po chen po'ang de yin te /
NK105(be)002:19150: rdzogs sangs sku ni 'phro phyir dang //
NK105(be)002:19151: de bzhin nyid dbyer med phyir dang //
NK105(be)002:19152: rigs yod phyir na lus can kun //
NK105(be)002:19153: rtag tu sangs rgyas snying po can //
NK105(be)002:19156: gang zhig gang la gnas pa de dag ni //
NK105(be)002:19157: de ni de ru mthong bar ma gyur te //
NK105(be)002:19158: mkhas pa thams cad bstan bcos 'chad pa yis //
NK105(be)002:19159: lus la sangs rgyas yod pa ma rtogs so //
NK105(be)002:19161: 'di nyid ye shes kyi rtsa zhes bya ste /
NK105(be)002:19162: rlung sems kyi dngas ma thams cad der 'dus pa'i
NK105(be)002:19163: tshe mya ngan las 'das pa'i zhing snang lhun grub
NK105(be)002:19164: 'od kyi khang pa bar do ye shes kyi sgron
NK105(be)002:19166: 'og min gyi zhing rnam dag stug po bkod pa zhes bya ba de yin pas na /
NK105(be)002:19167: rnal 'byor bas 'bad pa na rlung sems kyi dngas
NK105(be)002:19168: ma thams cad der rdzogs nas snang cha 'od lnga
NK105(be)002:19169: dang stong cha chos kyi sku ro gcig tu 'dres
NK105(be)002:19170: pas / lam tshogs gnyis rdzogs te sku gnyis mngon
NK105(be)002:19171: du gyur pas 'og min du sangs rgyas pa zhes
NK105(be)002:19172: pas / bya'o // de'ang dbu ma'i nang na ye
NK105(be)002:19173: shes kyi 'od rtsa yod par bshad pa de dang
NK105(be)002:19175: sems nyid 'od gsal ba'i rten yin par gcig pa'i phyir ro //
NK105(be)002:19177: dbu ma nas snying dbus su 'od lam shin tu
NK105(be)002:19178: phra ba rta rnga bcur gshags tsam zang thal le
NK105(be)002:19179: yod par 'brel te rten byas pa yin no //
NK105(be)002:19180: slob dpon kha cig dbu ma yang dag pa de nyid yin pas /
NK105(be)002:19181: rtsa gsum dbu ma'i nang dang 'brel mi dgos so zhes kyang 'chad do //
NK105(be)002:19182: 'on kyang rlung thams cad dbu mar 'jug la /
NK105(be)002:19183: dbu ma'i rlung gi dngas ma ye shes kyi rtsa der 'jug dgos pas 'brel bar 'thad cing /
NK105(be)002:19184: 'chi dus dngas ma dang rlung thams cad dbu mar 'du /
NK105(be)002:19185: dbu ma'i rlung dang dngas ma'i shin tu dngas ma
NK105(be)002:19186: der 'dus pa las 'od gsal 'char bar 'dod de
NK105(be)002:19190: nye bar thob pa bzhi rim pas shar zhing nub
NK105(be)002:19191: nas snang ba'i 'od gsal ye shes lnga'i zhing snang
NK105(be)002:19192: gis nam mkha' khyab par 'char zhing /
NK105(be)002:19193: rigs lnga'i sku dang zhing khams bsam gtan gyi zhag
NK105(be)002:19194: lngar 'char bar gsungs pa rnams de'i gnad kyis byung
NK105(be)002:19195: ba yin no // des na gnad 'di ni shin tu gsang ba'i gsang chen dam pa yin no //
NK105(be)002:19196: de lta bu'i rtsa nang gi khrag dbugs dngas ma'i
NK105(be)002:19197: 'od lnga'i klong na bzhugs pa'i byang chub kyi sems
NK105(be)002:19198: de yang / dper na gser gyi sbu gu'i nang
NK105(be)002:19199: du nor bu ke ke ru bcug pa ltar dngas
NK105(be)002:19204: de ltar rtsa'i dngas ma rtsa phran rgyus pa bldad pa 'dra ba brgyad yod pa la bya'o //
NK105(be)002:19205: de'i dbyibs pa thag khug pa bzhin du 'dug pa la brgyad ces bya'o //
NK105(be)002:19206: de ltar brgyad kyi mdo dngas ma'i yang rtsa'i dngas
NK105(be)002:19207: ma dar dkar gyi skud pa 'dra ba la dbyibs
NK105(be)002:19208: pa thag gug pa 'dra ba zhig yod la /
NK105(be)002:19209: de'i phra sbom ni rta rnga bcu tshal tsam gyis bzung la /
NK105(be)002:19210: dar dkar gyi skud pa 'dra ba de la khrag
NK105(be)002:19211: gi dngas ma mtshal lcog la ma'i dngas ma 'dra
NK105(be)002:19212: ba zhig rgyu'o // de la dbugs kyi dngas ma
NK105(be)002:19213: gser sa le sbram sa 'og na gnas pa'i rlangs
NK105(be)002:19214: ba zhig rgyu'o // pa tsam rgyu'o // dbugs kyi
NK105(be)002:19215: dngas ma de la 'od kha dog sna tshogs pa
NK105(be)002:19216: ba zhig rgyu'o // pa tsam rgyu'o // zhig gnas so // 'od de'i nang la dkyil zhes bya'o //
NK105(be)002:19217: na zhes pa bzhugs pa'i don te /
NK105(be)002:19218: 'od de'i dkyil na thig le chen po byang chub kyi sems bzhugs so //
NK105(be)002:19220: gser zhun ma'i sbu gu'i nang du nor bu rin po che'i ze'u ka btsugs pa'am /
NK105(be)002:19221: rin po che ke ke ru gdang la gtams pa 'dra la /
NK105(be)002:19222: kha dog nyi ma shar ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dra bar bzhugs so //
NK105(be)002:19223: de ni chos kyi dbyings kyi snying po don dam dang kun rdzob kyi rgyu yin pas /
NK105(be)002:19224: de la phyag 'tshal lo zhes bya'o zhes gsungs so //
NK105(be)002:19225: de lta bu'i sems nyid 'od gsal ba kun la
NK105(be)002:19226: khyab pas sems can thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas
NK105(be)002:19227: pa yin la / 'khor bar 'khyams kyang sems de la g.yo ba'am /
NK105(be)002:19229: dman par gyur pa med cing /
NK105(be)002:19230: sangs rgyas pas kyang sngon bas bzang du song ba med de /
NK105(be)002:19232: ji ltar sngar bzhin phyis de bzhin //
NK105(be)002:19233: 'gyur ba med pa'i chos nyid do //
NK105(be)002:19236: byang chub kyi sems kyi sprin gyis thams cad la
NK105(be)002:19237: rgyas par khyab pa ni til 'bru la mar gyis
NK105(be)002:19240: e ma'o ye nas rnam dag chos //
NK105(be)002:19241: sna tshogs snang yang rtog pa gsang //
NK105(be)002:19242: ngo bo nyid ni brjod du med //
NK105(be)002:19243: snod ma yin la bstan par daka'o //
NK105(be)002:19245: srid gsum ye nas dag pa'i rang bzhin la //
NK105(be)002:19246: bdag tu rtog pa'i srid rtsa'i nyes dmigs kyis //
NK105(be)002:19247: yun ring dus nas 'khyams pa'i 'gro ba rnams //
NK105(be)002:19248: mi mthun bde sdug gnas rnams so sor bzung //
NK105(be)002:19249: log rtog nor ba'i dbang gis kun brtags kyang //
NK105(be)002:19250: rang bzhin nyid las nyams pa rdul tsam med //
NK105(be)002:19252: yun ring dus nas rmongs pa'i 'gro ba rnams //
NK105(be)002:19253: ye nas don gyi sangs rgyas yin mod kyang //
NK105(be)002:19254: rmongs pa'i dbang gis 'khor ba'i 'khor lor 'khyams //
NK105(be)002:19255: log rtog nyid nas dngos med byang chub sems //
NK105(be)002:19256: 'khrul 'khor nyid kyang mi zad rgyan du che //
NK105(be)002:19257: snyigs ma lnga nyid bde ldan gnas su gsal //
NK105(be)002:19258: phung po lnga nyid mngon par rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK105(be)002:19259: srid rtsa'i nyes dmigs byang chub snying por gsal //
NK105(be)002:19260: phyi nang snod bcud yab yum ngang du gsal //
NK105(be)002:19261: zhes gsungs pas chos thams cad byang chub kyi sems su gnas so zhes so //
NK105(be)002:19262: de ltar ma dag pa sems can gyi 'khrul tshul bstan zin to //
NK105(be)002:19263: da ni de thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas par bstan pa ni /
NK105(be)002:19264: 'di ltar ma dag pa ltar snang ba'i phung po lnga yab lnga'i rang bzhin du sangs rgyas zhing /
NK105(be)002:19265: 'byung ba lnga yum lnga'i rang bzhin du sangs rgyas la /
NK105(be)002:19266: rtog tshogs thams cad byang chub sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor
NK105(be)002:19267: du sangs rgyas pas sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan pa'i
NK105(be)002:19268: chos rdul tsam yang med de /
NK105(be)002:19271: rdo rje phung po'i yan lag ni //
NK105(be)002:19272: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas lnga ru grags //
NK105(be)002:19273: skye mched khams rnams mang po kun //
NK105(be)002:19274: byang chub sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor nyid //
NK105(be)002:19275: sa chu spyan dang m+aa ma k+ai //
NK105(be)002:19276: me rlung gos dkar sgrol ma ste //
NK105(be)002:19277: nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK105(be)002:19278: srid gsum ye nas sangs rgyas zhing //
NK105(be)002:19279: thams cad ma lus chos so cog /
NK105(be)002:19280: sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan ma yin //
NK105(be)002:19281: sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan pa'i chos //
NK105(be)002:19282: sangs rgyas nyid kyis mi brnyes so //
NK105(be)002:19284: khyad par du sems nyid 'od gsal ba nyid sangs rgyas yin par /
NK105(be)002:19286: sems las ma gtogs pa yi sangs rgyas ni //
NK105(be)002:19287: kun byed rgyal pos sngar yang lung ma bstan //
NK105(be)002:19288: phyis nas mi ston da lta ston mi mdzad //
NK105(be)002:19289: des na sangs rgyas sems su shes par bya //
NK105(be)002:19292: rin chen sems las phyir gyur pa'i //
NK105(be)002:19293: sangs rgyas med cing sems can med //
NK105(be)002:19296: sems kyi dam pa 'od gsal ba //
NK105(be)002:19297: kun du dang po'i sangs rgyas te //
NK105(be)002:19298: sus kyang ma byas rang byung ba //
NK105(be)002:19299: ye nyid nas ni gnas pa'o //
NK105(be)002:19301: mdor na snang ba thams cad sku'i dkyil 'khor /
NK105(be)002:19302: grag pa thams cad gsung gi dkyil 'khor /
NK105(be)002:19303: dran rig thams cad thugs kyi dkyil 'khor te gsum du shes par bya ba yang /
NK105(be)002:19305: kye ston pa'i ston pa kun byed rgyal po yis //
NK105(be)002:19306: snying po sku yi dkyil 'khor bkod pa ni //
NK105(be)002:19307: ji ltar snang zhing gnas pa'i chos rnams kun //
NK105(be)002:19308: skye ba med pa'i chos dbyings ngang la bkod //
NK105(be)002:19309: ji ltar grags shing gnas pa'i chos rnams kun //
NK105(be)002:19310: skye med dbyings la tshig gis gsung du bkod //
NK105(be)002:19311: snying po brjod du med pa'i gsung la 'dus //
NK105(be)002:19312: de yang kun byed rgyal pos bkod pa yin //
NK105(be)002:19313: kye ston pa'i ston pa kun byed rgyal po yis //
NK105(be)002:19314: snying po rig pa'i dkyil 'khor bkod pa ni //
NK105(be)002:19315: ji ltar dran rig rtog pa thams cad kun //
NK105(be)002:19316: ma skyes kun byed nyid kyi don du rig /
NK105(be)002:19317: kun byed nga yi sku gsung thugs nyid ni //
NK105(be)002:19318: ma bcos rnal du bzhag pa'i dkyil 'khor gsum //
NK105(be)002:19319: ma bkod dus gcig rdzogs pa'i don rtogs pas //
NK105(be)002:19320: lhun grub snying po'i don la 'jug par byed //
NK105(be)002:19322: de'ang sna tshogs su snang ba nyid ni bskyed pa yin la /
NK105(be)002:19323: rang bzhin med pas rdzogs pa yin te /
NK105(be)002:19324: gzhi don gyi dkyil 'khor ni bskyed bya skyed byed dang bral bar shes par bya'o //
NK105(be)002:19327: kye kun byed nga yi dkyil 'khor bstan pa ni //
NK105(be)002:19328: rang las byung ba'i dkyil 'khor rdzogs pa'i lung //
NK105(be)002:19329: ma lus snying por rdzogs pa'i skye 'bri med //
NK105(be)002:19330: ma bskyed dus gcig rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor rtogs //
NK105(be)002:19331: kye dkyil ni ma nor don gyi snying po la //
NK105(be)002:19332: 'khor ni 'khor 'das bde chen rdzogs par ldan //
NK105(be)002:19333: de ni dkyil 'khor snying po kun gyi rtsa //
NK105(be)002:19334: dkyil 'khor ma lus 'di la 'dus par rtogs //
NK105(be)002:19335: kye kun byed rgyal po nga yi dkyil 'khor ni //
NK105(be)002:19336: ma lus snying por rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor te //
NK105(be)002:19337: gang gis de dag rdzogs par gang rtogs pa //
NK105(be)002:19338: dkyil 'khor bskyed du med pa'i don la mkhas //
NK105(be)002:19339: kye ston pa'i ston pa kun byed rgyal po ngas //
NK105(be)002:19340: skye med byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor gyis //
NK105(be)002:19341: 'gro dang 'ong med kun du khyab par gdal //
NK105(be)002:19342: rtogs pas skye ba med pa'i don la 'jug /
NK105(be)002:19343: de phyir sems dpa' rdo rje khyod kyis kyang //
NK105(be)002:19344: sgra la ma gnas don nyid rtogs par gyis //
NK105(be)002:19345: gang gis de la rtogs pa skyes ma thag /
NK105(be)002:19346: kun byed rgyal po'i don la dbang 'byor 'gyur //
NK105(be)002:19348: de ltar na snang tshod pa'i ngos nas phung po
NK105(be)002:19349: dang khams dang skye mched la sogs pa thams cad
NK105(be)002:19350: lha'i rang bzhin du sangs rgyas pas bzang ngan dang
NK105(be)002:19352: de dag ni stong pa chos nyid kyi ngos nas
NK105(be)002:19353: yod med kyi spros pa nye bar zhi ba ni
NK105(be)002:19354: gzhi rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor chen
NK105(be)002:19355: po ste / de ltar rtogs pas ni snang srid
NK105(be)002:19356: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad dkyil 'khor du shes
NK105(be)002:19357: pas ci snang ye shes su skyong ba yin te
NK105(be)002:19359: rdzogs chen rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK105(be)002:19362: de dag gis dang po lta bas gtan la dbab pa bstan zin to //
NK105(be)002:19363: spyi don gnyis pa sgom pas nyams su len pa smin grol spyod pa dang bcas pa bshad pa'i /
NK105(be)002:19364: bskyed rim bsgom pa'i tshul mdor bstan pa la lnga las /
NK105(be)002:19365: sgong skyes kyi tshul ltar bsgom pa ni /
NK105(be)002:19366: gnyis pa sgom pas nyams su blang ba la /
NK105(be)002:19367: gzhi smin byed dbang gi rim pa dang /
NK105(be)002:19368: lam grol byed bskyed rdzogs kyi rim pa dang /
NK105(be)002:19369: de'i grogs spyod pa dang dam tshig rgya cher bshad pa gsum las /
NK105(be)002:19370: re zhig bskyed rim bsgom pa'i tshul bshad pa /
NK105(be)002:19371: de yang skye bzhi'i rim pas bsgom tshul bzhi //
NK105(be)002:19372: sgong skyes bag chags sbyang phyir sngon 'gro'i tshe //
NK105(be)002:19373: skyabs 'gro sems bskyed bskyed rim mdor bsdus nas //
NK105(be)002:19374: bsod nams zhing rab spyan drangs mchod pa'i mthar //
NK105(be)002:19375: rang bzhin med bsgom tshogs gnyis sngon song nas //
NK105(be)002:19376: gdod kyis bskyed rdzogs rgyas par bsgom pa ni //
NK105(be)002:19377: thog mar sgo nga de las bya skye bzhin //
NK105(be)002:19378: mdor bsdus rgyas pa'i bskyed rdzogs rim pas bsgom //
NK105(be)002:19379: de la gsang sngags kyi rim pa dang po bskyed
NK105(be)002:19380: pa lha'i ting nge 'dzin ji snyed bsgom pa de
NK105(be)002:19381: dag skye gnas bzhi'i bag chags sbyong ba dang bstun
NK105(be)002:19384: skye gnas bzhi po dag bya'i phyir //
NK105(be)002:19385: bskyed pa'ang de bzhin rnam pa bzhi //
NK105(be)002:19386: spros can spros dang spros pa med //
NK105(be)002:19387: shin tu spros pa med bzhi'o //
NK105(be)002:19388: zhes pa'i tshul slob dpon chen po bi ma las gsal bar phye ba ltar bshad par bya ste /
NK105(be)002:19389: 'di ltar sgo nga las skye ba rnams ni lan gnyis skye ba ltar /
NK105(be)002:19390: spros pa chen po'i ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa gang gi tshe /
NK105(be)002:19391: thog mar skyabs su 'gro ba dang sems bskyed pa dang /
NK105(be)002:19392: rang nyid skad cig gis gtso bo yab yum du gsal gdab pa rnams byas la /
NK105(be)002:19393: mdun gyi nam mkhar lha'i dkyil 'khor spyan drangs te /
NK105(be)002:19398: 'khor lo bskor bar bskul ba dang /
NK105(be)002:19399: 'dod pa'i don la gsol ba gdab pa dang /
NK105(be)002:19400: bsod nams bsngo ba rnams byas la /
NK105(be)002:19401: badz+ra muhs gshegs su gsol ba'am /
NK105(be)002:19402: mi dmigs par bsgoms pa'i ngang la dar cig mnyam
NK105(be)002:19403: par gzhag pa ni bsod nams dang ye shes kyi
NK105(be)002:19404: tshogs gsog pa ste mdor bsdus pa'o //
NK105(be)002:19405: de nas stong pa'i ngang las lha so so'i dkyil 'khor rgyas par bsgom pa ni rgyas pa'o //
NK105(be)002:19406: mngal skyes kyi tshul ltar bsgom pa ni /
NK105(be)002:19407: de las cung zad spros pa chung ba /
NK105(be)002:19408: mngal skyes bag chags sbyang phyir bstan pa ni //
NK105(be)002:19409: skyabs 'gro sems bskyed stong las sa bon dang //
NK105(be)002:19410: phyag mtshan las ni sku dang 'od zer sogs //
NK105(be)002:19411: rim gyis rgyas par bsgom gyi sngar bzhin du //
NK105(be)002:19412: mdor bsdus sngon du mi 'gro'i bskyed rdzogs ni //
NK105(be)002:19413: ji ltar rlung sems thig le dkar dmar las //
NK105(be)002:19414: mer nur ltar dang mkhrang gyur la sogs nas //
NK105(be)002:19415: lus yongs rdzogs te btsa' ba'i bar bzhin no //
NK105(be)002:19416: 'di ltar mngal las skye ba dag rim gyis lus rdzogs pas skye ba ltar /
NK105(be)002:19417: bskyed pa'i rim pa de yang dang po skyabs su 'gro ba dang sems bskyed nas /
NK105(be)002:19418: swa b+h+aa was stong pa'i ngang las thig le dkar dmar 'dus par rnam shes zhugs pa ltar /
NK105(be)002:19419: lha'i sa bon h+aum lta bu dang /
NK105(be)002:19420: mer mer po dang nur nur po ltar h+aum las rdo rje dang /
NK105(be)002:19421: ltar ltar po dang mkhrang gyur ltar rdo rje las sku de'i rgyu 'od lnga'i gong bu dang /
NK105(be)002:19422: khyab 'jug nya dang rus sbal nas lus byin rdzogs
NK105(be)002:19423: pa ltar 'od las skur gyur pa nas bskyed pa'i
NK105(be)002:19424: rim pa rdzogs par bsgom pa'o //
NK105(be)002:19425: kha cig ni sa bon las 'od kyi gong bu dang /
NK105(be)002:19426: phyag mtshan las skur bzhengs par 'dod de /
NK105(be)002:19427: de'ang bskyed rim mdor bsdus pa dang /
NK105(be)002:19428: bsod nams kyi zhing mchod pa rnams bor bas spros pa chung ba yin no //
NK105(be)002:19429: drod gsher skyes kyi tshul ltar bsgom pa ni /
NK105(be)002:19431: drod gsher las skyes bag chags sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK105(be)002:19432: skyabs 'gro sems bskyed stong las lha rnams kyi //
NK105(be)002:19433: mtshan tsam brjod las lhar gsal bskyed rdzogs bsgom /
NK105(be)002:19434: ji ltar drod gsher 'dus las grub pa'i lus //
NK105(be)002:19435: shin tu 'grub par sla bas btsa' ba bzhin //
NK105(be)002:19436: sa bon phyag mtshan spros pa dgos pa med //
NK105(be)002:19437: 'di ltar drod gsher las skye ba ni 'grub par sla ba ltar /
NK105(be)002:19438: skyabs su 'gro ba dang sems bskyed la /
NK105(be)002:19439: stong pa'i ngang las lha'i mtshan tsam brjod pa'am dran pa las bskyed pa'o //
NK105(be)002:19440: de'ang sa bon nas sku'i bar gyi spros pa rnams dor ba yin no //
NK105(be)002:19441: bardzusa skyes kyi tshul ltar bsgom pa ni /
NK105(be)002:19443: bardzusa te skye ba'i bag chags sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK105(be)002:19444: skad cig tsam gyis wal gyis bskyed rdzogs bsgom //
NK105(be)002:19445: ji ltar bardzusa skyes skad cig snang ba bzhin //
NK105(be)002:19446: ming las rim gyis bskyed rdzogs bsgom mi dgos //
NK105(be)002:19447: 'di ltar bardzusa te skye ba skad cig gis 'grub pa ltar /
NK105(be)002:19448: lha yang dran rdzogs su wal gyis sgom gyi ming
NK105(be)002:19449: las lhar bskyed pa tsam gyi spros pa bsgom mi
NK105(be)002:19450: dgos so // gtso bor bsgom tshul ni /
NK105(be)002:19452: de ltar sgom tshul rnam pa bzhi nyid kyang //
NK105(be)002:19453: gtso bor skye ba gang bsdus des bsgoms la //
NK105(be)002:19454: bag chags sbyang phyir kun gyis de bzhin bsgom //
NK105(be)002:19455: khyad par las dang po yis sgong skyes bzhin //
NK105(be)002:19456: cung zad brtan pas mngal skyes bzhin bsgoms la //
NK105(be)002:19457: brtan pa che bas drod gsher skyes bzhin bsgom //
NK105(be)002:19458: shin tu goms pa yang dag brtan pa yis //
NK105(be)002:19459: bardzusa skyes bzhin du skad cig dkrongs bskyed bya //
NK105(be)002:19460: 'di ltar mi rnams kyis ni sgom tshul kun la bslab cing /
NK105(be)002:19461: mngal skyes bzhin gtso cher byas la /
NK105(be)002:19462: las dang po pa la sogs pa'i rim pas rim gyis bsgom zhing /
NK105(be)002:19463: skye ba gang bsdus des de'i bsgom tshul la bslab bo //
NK105(be)002:19464: gzhan yang bskyed rim mang du bsgoms nas rdzogs rim la gtso bor slob pas /
NK105(be)002:19468: bzhi par goms pa bzhi la sgom tshul de nyid rim pa bzhin sngon du 'gro bar bya'o //
NK105(be)002:19469: rdzogs rim la 'jug tshul la bzhi las /
NK105(be)002:19470: snang bcas snang med kyi tshul ni /
NK105(be)002:19471: da ni rdzogs pa'i rim pa la 'jug par bya ste /
NK105(be)002:19472: rdzogs rim de yang snang bcas snang med de //
NK105(be)002:19473: bskyed rim bsdus nas mkha' la sprin dengs bzhin //
NK105(be)002:19474: mi dmigs ngang du 'jog pa snang ba med //
NK105(be)002:19475: bskyed rim de nyid rdzogs par shes bya ste //
NK105(be)002:19476: snang dus nyid nas rang bzhin spros dang bral //
NK105(be)002:19477: ma yengs bsgom pa snang bcas rim pa bzhin //
NK105(be)002:19478: las dang po yis bskyed rim zhen pa dgag /
NK105(be)002:19479: snang la bden par zhen pa'i gnyen po byed //
NK105(be)002:19480: brtan pa rnams kyis rdzogs rim zhen pa dgag /
NK105(be)002:19481: stong la mtshan mar zhen pa'i gnyen po byed //
NK105(be)002:19482: 'di ltar rim gyis bsdus nas n+aa da dang bin
NK105(be)002:19483: d+hu ste shin tu phra ba'i srog gi yi ge
NK105(be)002:19484: rta rnga brgyar gshags pa tsam la bsdu /
NK105(be)002:19485: de chos kyi dbyings su thim pa'i ngang la 'jog
NK105(be)002:19486: pa ni snang ba med pa'i rdzogs rim las dang
NK105(be)002:19487: po pa dag gis bsgom pa ste /
NK105(be)002:19488: bskyed pa'i rim pa dngos po rang mtshan du zhen pa'i rtog pa 'joms so //
NK105(be)002:19489: bskyed rim gyi ngang las sems ma yengs par spro
NK105(be)002:19490: bsdu med par gzhag pas bde gsal mi rtog pa'i
NK105(be)002:19491: ye shes 'char ba ni snang ba dang bcas pa'i
NK105(be)002:19492: rdzogs rim ste / cung zad goms pa brtan pa rnams kyi spyod yul yin zhing /
NK105(be)002:19493: stong ba mtha' gcig tu zhen pa'i gnyen po byed do //
NK105(be)002:19494: bskyed rdzogs 'du 'bral med par 'char tshul ni /
NK105(be)002:19496: phyi nas gang snang bskyed rim thabs nyid la //
NK105(be)002:19497: 'dzin med shes pa rdzogs rim shes rab nyid //
NK105(be)002:19498: dus rnams kun du 'du 'bral med pa 'char //
NK105(be)002:19499: de yang snga ma ltar goms pa shin tu brtan
NK105(be)002:19500: pas spyod lam thams cad du snang stong grag stong
NK105(be)002:19501: rig stong gi chos nyid bden med kyi shes rab
NK105(be)002:19502: dang / ngang gis mi rtog pa'i zhi gnas dbyer
NK105(be)002:19503: med pa 'char ba ni rang bzhin dag pa'i rdzogs
NK105(be)002:19504: dang / rim mo // gzhan yang gzhung so so'i
NK105(be)002:19505: skabs su rgyud sde so so'i rdzogs rim de lta
NK105(be)002:19506: bu dang mthun par bstan pa ni spyi'i dbang du
NK105(be)002:19507: dang / rim mo // byas pa'o // rnal 'byor chen po'i gzhung 'ga' zhig las /
NK105(be)002:19508: bdag byin gyis brlab pa'i rim pa /
NK105(be)002:19509: sna tshogs rdo rje'i rim pa /
NK105(be)002:19511: dza lan d+ha ra'i rim pa /
NK105(be)002:19512: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i rim pa dang lngar gsungs te /
NK105(be)002:19513: de'ang dang por zhi gnas bskyed pa'i phyir bskyed rim
NK105(be)002:19514: bsgoms pa'i snying nang du thig le 'od kyi gong
NK105(be)002:19516: rlung phyir rgyu ba 'byung ba lnga'i kha dog gi
NK105(be)002:19517: dus kyi rjes su 'gro ba dang mthun par bsgoms
NK105(be)002:19518: la nad gdon sdig sgrib thams cad phyir bsang /
NK105(be)002:19519: nang du 'jug pa'i tshe sangs rgyas la sogs pa'i
NK105(be)002:19520: yon tan gyi dngos grub dang mnyam du snying ga'i
NK105(be)002:19522: myur du bde gsal mi rtog pa'i ye shes grub
NK105(be)002:19523: pas thun mong dang mchog gi dngos grub 'grub pa
NK105(be)002:19525: rtag tu snying la gnas pa yi //
NK105(be)002:19526: thig le gcig la 'gyur ba med //
NK105(be)002:19527: de sgom byed pa'i skye bo la //
NK105(be)002:19528: nges par ye shes skye bar 'gyur //
NK105(be)002:19530: thig le ni sngar bshad zin to //
NK105(be)002:19531: sna tshogs rdo rje'i rim pa ni /
NK105(be)002:19532: rlung kha sbyar te 'khor lo lnga'i dbus su rigs lnga'i phyag mtshan bsgom ste /
NK105(be)002:19537: gsang bar ral gri bsgoms la phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas
NK105(be)002:19538: la sogs pa rigs lnga rang rang gi phyag mtshan
NK105(be)002:19539: la thim par sems bzung la bsgoms pas zhi gnas
NK105(be)002:19540: skye'o // nor bu 'gengs pa'i rim pa ni /
NK105(be)002:19541: lhan cig rol pa'i bde ba chen pos 'khor lo
NK105(be)002:19542: bzhi'i nang nas dga' ba bzhi'i ye shes bskyed cing
NK105(be)002:19543: ye shes ngos 'dzin pa yin no //
NK105(be)002:19544: dza lan d+ha ra'i rim pa ni /
NK105(be)002:19545: rigs lnga'i phyag mtshan skur gyur pa yab yum gyi
NK105(be)002:19546: sbyor mtshams nas bdud rtsi bab pas lus khengs par
NK105(be)002:19547: bsgoms la / gtum mo'i mes ham bsregs pa'i bde ba la sems 'dzin pa ste /
NK105(be)002:19548: gtum mo'i ye shes me 'od kyis //
NK105(be)002:19549: de bzhin gshegs pa'i khams bsregs te //
NK105(be)002:19552: gtum mo lte bar sbar ba yis //
NK105(be)002:19553: tshigs thams cad ni bsreg pa ste //
NK105(be)002:19554: mig la sogs pa bsregs nas ni //
NK105(be)002:19555: bsregs pas rkan las thig le 'dzag /'gro 'o de ni mtshams kun du //
NK105(be)002:19556: pang snal skud pa'i dra ba'o //
NK105(be)002:19558: stong phrag bdun cu rtsa gnyis la'o //
NK105(be)002:19560: des zung 'jug gi rtogs pa dang ting nge 'dzin 'phel ba yin no //
NK105(be)002:19561: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i rim pa ni /
NK105(be)002:19562: snying ga'i 'od kyi gong bu'i dbus su h'u la
NK105(be)002:19563: sogs pa lha so so'i sa bon bsams pa las
NK105(be)002:19564: 'od 'phros 'khor 'das thams cad la phog sangs rgyas
NK105(be)002:19565: dang sems can brtan g.yo'i khams thams cad 'od du
NK105(be)002:19566: zhu ba snying ga'i 'od la thim /
NK105(be)002:19567: lus dang 'od kyang h+aum yin na zhabs kyu /
NK105(be)002:19572: thig le n+aa da ste bin+d+hu'i dbyings mi dmigs pa nam mkha'i ngang la bzhag go //
NK105(be)002:19574: snga ma bzhin gcig las gcig mched du bsgom zhing
NK105(be)002:19575: yang thim par bsgom pa ni chos nyid bsam gyis
NK105(be)002:19576: mi khyab pa'i don lhag mthong dang zhi gnas zung
NK105(be)002:19578: 'di dag las dang po pas rim gyis bslab pa dang /
NK105(be)002:19579: sbyangs pa byas pas gang rgyud la skye sla ba
NK105(be)002:19580: de nas bslab par gsungs pas go rims kho na'i
NK105(be)002:19582: bskyed rdzogs bsgoms pa'i byed pa ni /
NK105(be)002:19583: de ltar bskyed rdzogs bsgoms pa'i tshul des ci bya zhe na /
NK105(be)002:19584: bskyed rim snang 'di'i bden zhen 'gog pa ste //
NK105(be)002:19585: rdzogs rim sgyu mar zhen pa'i rtog pa spong //
NK105(be)002:19586: gang la snang stong bden zhen med pa na //
NK105(be)002:19587: bskyed rdzogs gnyis med rang bzhin dag pa yin //
NK105(be)002:19588: de la bskyed pa'i rim pas phyi snod gzhal yas
NK105(be)002:19589: khang du bsgoms pas sa rdo rang mtshan pa la
NK105(be)002:19590: sogs pa tha mal gyi yul snang du 'dzin pa
NK105(be)002:19591: spong / sems can lha dang lha mor bsgoms pas
NK105(be)002:19592: sems can rang mtshan pa'i bden zhen dang chags sdang
NK105(be)002:19593: spong / spong / rang nyid kyi phung po khams
NK105(be)002:19594: dang skye mched lhar gsal bas ye nas de yin
NK105(be)002:19595: pa gsal thebs pas gzugs sku'i sgrib pa sbyong ba
NK105(be)002:19596: spong / spong / dang / bsod nams kyi tshogs rdzogs pa dang /
NK105(be)002:19597: zhi gnas kyi ting nge 'dzin skye ba la sogs pa dgos pa du ma yod do //
NK105(be)002:19598: de'ang rnal 'a byor gyi rgyud la sogs pa sngags phyi pa gsum la /
NK105(be)002:19599: bskyed rim phyag rgya bzhis rgyas gdab pa dang /
NK105(be)002:19600: dran pa nye bar gzhag pa bzhi bsgom pa dang /
NK105(be)002:19601: sgyu ma lta bur bsgom pa dang /
NK105(be)002:19602: thun rjes bsdu ba rnams 'byung gi //
NK105(be)002:19603: zab pa'i rim pa chen po rnams ni med do //
NK105(be)002:19604: bla med kyi rgyud du ni thabs dang shes rab bsam gyis mi khyab pa gsungs so //
NK105(be)002:19605: rdzogs pa'i rim pa bsgoms pas ni sngar bskyed rim
NK105(be)002:19606: dang chos thams cad sgyu ma lta bur bsgoms pa'i
NK105(be)002:19607: zhen pa cung zad yod pa'ang spong zhing /
NK105(be)002:19608: 'di dang 'adi'o zhes pa'i dmigs bsam thams cad dang
NK105(be)002:19609: bral bas chos sku'i sgrib pa dag nas bsam gyis
NK105(be)002:19610: mi khyab pa'i ting nge 'dzin ye shes kyi tshogs
NK105(be)002:19612: de'ang rdzogs rim gyi ngo bo ni dmigs pa 'ga'
NK105(be)002:19613: zhig gi steng du sems rtse gcig tu bzhag pas
NK105(be)002:19614: bde gsal mi rtog pa'i ngang la gnas te gnyug
NK105(be)002:19615: ma phyag rgya chen po'i don rtogs pa la sbyor
NK105(be)002:19616: ba'o // de'ang gshis kyi yin tshul la /
NK105(be)002:19618: rdo rje'i lus kyi rang bzhin /
NK105(be)002:19619: sems nyid don gyi ngo bo rnams shes nas sgom par byed pa ste /
NK105(be)002:19620: de'ang rang lus thabs ldan dang /
NK105(be)002:19621: gzhan lus rig ma la brten pa gnyis so //
NK105(be)002:19628: 'pho ba la sogs pa rang gi sems kyi rtsol
NK105(be)002:19629: thabs gzhan la rag ma lus par byang chub bsgrub
NK105(be)002:19632: rtsa rlung thig le gnad du song ba'i rnal 'byor pas bde ba lam du byed pa'o //
NK105(be)002:19634: bskyed rim gyi zhen pa spangs pas lha chos nyid du rtogs pa dang /
NK105(be)002:19635: thabs khyad par can gyis bde gsal mi rtog pa skye ba dang /
NK105(be)002:19636: thams cad lam du 'gro bas cir snang chos nyid du 'char ba dang /
NK105(be)002:19637: rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes rtogs pas
NK105(be)002:19638: gnas lugs kyi phu thag 'khrus pa la sogs pa
NK105(be)002:19640: sangs rgyas kyi nye lam du bstan pa ni /
NK105(be)002:19642: 'di ni mthar thug rdo rje'i theg pa ste //
NK105(be)002:19643: dbang po rnon po tshe 'dir rdzogs sangs rgya //
NK105(be)002:19644: de rjes gdul bya'i 'jig rten gang yod der //
NK105(be)002:19645: sangs rgyas mdzad pa sna tshogs lhun gyis grub //
NK105(be)002:19646: 'di ni grangs med rdo rje 'chang rnams kyi //
NK105(be)002:19647: nye lam sbas pa shin tu zab mo ste //
NK105(be)002:19648: skal bzang tshe 'dir grol 'dod rnams kyis bsten //
NK105(be)002:19649: de lta bu'i lam ni dbang po shin tu rnon po tshe 'dir grol bas /
NK105(be)002:19650: de nas ring por mi thogs par sangs rgyas kyi
NK105(be)002:19651: mdzad pa chen po gdul bya gang na yod pa'i
NK105(be)002:19652: 'jig rten du lhun gyis grub par 'gyur te /
NK105(be)002:19653: rdo rje gsang ba'i rgyud las /
NK105(be)002:19654: bla med sngags kyi dngos grub gang //
NK105(be)002:19655: shin tu brtson pas gang bsgrubs pa //
NK105(be)002:19656: tshe 'di nyid la sangs rgyas te //
NK105(be)002:19657: gdul bya'i zhing du mdzad pa ston //
NK105(be)002:19658: grangs med rdo rje 'chang rnams kyi //
NK105(be)002:19659: zab mo'i nye lam mthar thug pa'o //
NK105(be)002:19661: de lta bu'i lam ni skal bzang thar pa 'dod
NK105(be)002:19662: pa rnams kyis bsten nas brtson 'grus chen pos 'bad
NK105(be)002:19663: par rigs so // gzhi smin byed dbang gi rim pa bstan pa la gsum las /
NK105(be)002:19664: spyi rang rang gi gzhung ltar blang ba ni /
NK105(be)002:19665: da ni gzhi smin byed dbang gi rim pa bstan pa ni /
NK105(be)002:19667: de yang gang mos rgyud sde'i rim pa la //
NK105(be)002:19668: brten nas rdzogs pa'i byang chub bsgrub par bya //
NK105(be)002:19669: thog mar rigs gtad rjes gnang dbang la sogs //
NK105(be)002:19670: rang rang gzhung nas gsungs pa'i lung mnos te //
NK105(be)002:19671: rang gi sems 'di yongs su smin par bya //
NK105(be)002:19672: de'ang a b+hi shiny+tsa'i sgra las dri ma bkru ba dang nus pa 'jog pas dbang zhes 'byung ste /
NK105(be)002:19673: slob ma'i rgyud kyi dri ma dag par byed cing
NK105(be)002:19674: ma 'ongs pa na sangs rgyas kyi byang chub dang
NK105(be)002:19675: gnas skabs so so'i lam bsgom pa'i nus pa la
NK105(be)002:19676: dbang bar byed pa yin no //
NK105(be)002:19677: de'ang rgyud sde so so nas byung ba'i rigs gtad pa'i cho ga dang /
NK105(be)002:19679: dbang sbyin pa la sogs pa ji skad bshad pa'i
NK105(be)002:19680: rim pa thob par byas nas de'i don nyams su
NK105(be)002:19681: len pa la 'jug pa yin no //
NK105(be)002:19682: de'ang k+r+ai ya'i rgyud las rigs gtad pa dang /
NK105(be)002:19684: man+dala tsam la brten nas bum pa'i chus dbang bskur
NK105(be)002:19685: sngags kyi rjes gnang sbyin pa tsam gyis lha bsgom
NK105(be)002:19686: pa'i snod du rung bar gsungs la /
NK105(be)002:19687: spyod pa'i rgyud nas rig pa'i dbang lnga rdo rje
NK105(be)002:19688: brtul zhugs kyi dbang dang drug bskur bas snod du
NK105(be)002:19690: rnal 'byor gyi rgyud nas rig pa'i dbang lngas thog
NK105(be)002:19691: drangs slob ma'i dbang dang rdo rje slob dpon gyi
NK105(be)002:19692: dbang rdzogs par bskur bas snod du rung bar bshad
NK105(be)002:19693: do // rnal 'byor bla na med pa'i rgyud nas
NK105(be)002:19694: bum dbang la sogs pa bzhi ka bskur bas lam
NK105(be)002:19695: bskyed pa'i rim pa dang rdzogs pa'i rim pa ma
NK105(be)002:19696: lus pa bsgom pa'i snod du rung bar bshad do
NK105(be)002:19697: do // // de'ang rdul tshon gyis dkyil 'khor ram /
NK105(be)002:19700: lus kyi dkyil 'khor la brten nas dbang bskur ba yin no //
NK105(be)002:19701: dbang po dman pas gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor /
NK105(be)002:19702: 'bring me tog gi tshom bu'am lha'i phyag mtshan la sogs pa dmigs rten cung zad tsam dang /
NK105(be)002:19703: rab lus kyi dkyil 'khor te bla ma'i sku gsung thugs la brten nas bskur ba'i tshul gsungs te /
NK105(be)002:19705: bcos ma gnyis kyi ngo bo gang //
NK105(be)002:19706: de ni gdul bya'i dbang las 'dod //
NK105(be)002:19708: grub pa'i dkyil 'khor gnyis med pa'o //
NK105(be)002:19710: bla na med pa'i dbang bzhi rdzogs su len tshul ni /
NK105(be)002:19712: khyad par mchog gsang rnal 'byor chen po'i lam //
NK105(be)002:19713: smin byed dbang bzhi grol byed bskyed rdzogs te //
NK105(be)002:19714: bum dbang lus dang gsang bas ngag dang ni //
NK105(be)002:19715: shes rab ye shes yid dang tshig dbang gis //
NK105(be)002:19716: bag chags mtha' dag sbyong zhing dngos grub ster //
NK105(be)002:19717: dang po gsum gyis bsod nams tshogs rdzogs la //
NK105(be)002:19718: bzhi pas ye shes tshogs rdzogs de bzhin du //
NK105(be)002:19719: nyon mongs pa dang shes bya'i sgrib kun sbyong //
NK105(be)002:19720: de phyir smin byed dbang bzhi thob pa yis //
NK105(be)002:19721: grol byed bskyed rdzogs don la bslab par bya //
NK105(be)002:19722: de la rnal 'byor chen po'i gzhung las dbang bzhir grags pa dag las /
NK105(be)002:19723: bum dbang gis lus kyi dri ma sbyong /
NK105(be)002:19724: bskyed pa'i rim pa bsgom pa la dbang /
NK105(be)002:19725: gsang bas ngag gi sgrib pa sbyong /
NK105(be)002:19726: gtum mo tsan+da l+ai bsgom pa la dbang /
NK105(be)002:19727: shes rab ye shes kyis yid kyi sgrib pa sbyong /
NK105(be)002:19728: bde stong rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes bsgom pa la dbang /
NK105(be)002:19729: tshig dbang rin po ches dri ma mtha' dag sbyong /
NK105(be)002:19730: gnas lugs phyag rgya chen po bsgom pa la dbang ngo //
NK105(be)002:19731: de'ang dang po gsum gyis bsod nams kyi tshogs rdzogs /
NK105(be)002:19733: bzhi pas ye shes kyi tshogs rdzogs /
NK105(be)002:19735: sa lam gyi dag pa dang sbyar na /
NK105(be)002:19738: shes rab ye shes kyis mthong lam /
NK105(be)002:19739: phyag rgya chen po don gyi dbang gis sgom lam rdzogs par byed pa yin no //
NK105(be)002:19740: de ltar dbang bzhi rdzogs pas smin par byas te /
NK105(be)002:19741: bskyed rdzogs gnyis bsgoms pas grol bar byed pa yin no //
NK105(be)002:19742: theg pa kun gyi rtse mor bstan pa ni /
NK105(be)002:19743: de ltar gsang sngags spyi'i rim pa bstan nas /
NK105(be)002:19744: bye brag tu sgyu 'phrul dra ba chen po gnyis
NK105(be)002:19745: su med pa'i rgyud sde kun gyi rtse mor gyur
NK105(be)002:19747: 'dir ni dbang rdzogs dam tshig ldan pa yis //
NK105(be)002:19748: gnyis med a ti'i dgongs par 'jug 'dod pas //
NK105(be)002:19750: de la dang po dbang gi rim pa ni /
NK105(be)002:19751: dman pa rnams rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK105(be)002:19752: mchog rnams 'jug pa la rdo rje slob dpon gyi
NK105(be)002:19753: lus kyi dkyil 'khor du 'jug par gsungs pas na
NK105(be)002:19754: / bde ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor yab yum gnyis kyi lus dkyil dang /
NK105(be)002:19755: rdul tshon rigs lnga'i rim pa nyid /
NK105(be)002:19757: bde ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK105(be)002:19758: stangs dpyal gnyis sam yang na lnga //
NK105(be)002:19759: byas te dad ldan rab zhugs na //
NK105(be)002:19762: de'ang phan pa'i dbang bcu dang /
NK105(be)002:19763: nus pa'i dbang lnga rdzogs par bya'o //
NK105(be)002:19766: dbu rgyan cod pan phreng ba dang //
NK105(be)002:19767: go cha rgyal mtshan phyag rgya dang //
NK105(be)002:19768: gdugs dang bum pa bza' btung dang //
NK105(be)002:19769: snying po lnga yis dbang bskur na //
NK105(be)002:19775: rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang /
NK105(be)002:19776: gsang ba mchog gi dbang dang lnga'o //
NK105(be)002:19777: dbang bco lnga po 'di dag kyang dbang bzhi'i dbye ba ste /
NK105(be)002:19778: bum pa la sogs pa bcu ni bum pa'i byed
NK105(be)002:19779: pa sngon du 'gro bas bum pa'i dbang yin la
NK105(be)002:19780: / gsang dbang las gsang ba dang shes rab ye shes kyi dbang 'byung zhing /
NK105(be)002:19781: tshig dbang ni rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyis bstan nas /
NK105(be)002:19782: 'chad pa dang phrin las gnyis de'i byed las kyi dbang dang /
NK105(be)002:19783: nyan pa ni gong du spel ba'i thabs yin pas der bsdu ba yin no //
NK105(be)002:19784: gzhan dag ni 'di dag sdud tshul tha dad pa
NK105(be)002:19785: gzhan byed pa'ang don la 'bab par ma mthong bas
NK105(be)002:19786: 'dir smi spro'o // de lta bu'i dbang rdzogs pa'am /
NK105(be)002:19787: yang na bla med kyi dbang de dang 'dra ba
NK105(be)002:19788: gzhan thob na'ang 'di'i lam nyams su len pa'i skal
NK105(be)002:19790: grogs spyod pa dang dam tshig gi rim pa 'phros don du bshad pa ni /
NK105(be)002:19791: da ni gsang sngags kyi spyod pa dang dam tshig gnyis las /
NK105(be)002:19792: dang po dbang dang 'brel bas dam tshig thog mar bshad de /
NK105(be)002:19793: de'ang dam tshig gi ngo bo ni /
NK105(be)002:19794: sngags la zhugs pa'i brtul zhugs bzang po mi nyams par bsrung ba'i lhag bsam khyad par can no //
NK105(be)002:19795: dbye na rtsa ba'i dam tshig dang /
NK105(be)002:19796: yan lag gi dam tshig go //
NK105(be)002:19798: sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig gsum ste /
NK105(be)002:19799: de'ang lus kyi dam tshig tu lha'i skur bsgom zhing
NK105(be)002:19800: lus kyi mi dge ba srog gcod ma byin len
NK105(be)002:19801: mi tshangs spyod la sogs pa cha dang bcas pa
NK105(be)002:19802: sdom pa'o // ngag gi dam tshig tu /
NK105(be)002:19803: sngags bzlas shing ngag gi mi dge ba bzhi cha dang bcas pa las bzlog pa'o //
NK105(be)002:19805: ting nge 'dzin zab mo bsgom zhing yid kyi mi
NK105(be)002:19806: dge ba gsum cha dang bcas pa las bzlog pa'o
NK105(be)002:19807: // mdor na lus ngag yid gsum tha mal pa'i
NK105(be)002:19808: rnam par lus na dam tshig nyams pas yang dag
NK105(be)002:19809: pa sku gsung thugs kyi rim pa las ma 'gal
NK105(be)002:19810: // bar bya'o // 'di dag cung zad rgyas par dbye na /
NK105(be)002:19811: dam tshig rnam par bkod pa sdom pa la 'jug pa'i 'khor lo las /
NK105(be)002:19812: 'gro ba'i smin so gsum dag las //
NK105(be)002:19813: sngags kyi dam tshig gsum du bshad //
NK105(be)002:19814: de la khyad par nges phye ba //
NK105(be)002:19815: sku dang gsung dang thugs dag las //
NK105(be)002:19816: re re la yang dgu dgu ste //
NK105(be)002:19817: 'jug dang las kyi rnam pas shes //
NK105(be)002:19819: de'ang 'gro ba rnams ye nas sangs rgyas su gnas
NK105(be)002:19820: pas sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig kyang yod de
NK105(be)002:19821: de nyid ma nyams pa las dngos grub 'byung ba'i
NK105(be)002:19822: phyir bsrung bar bya ba nyid de /
NK105(be)002:19823: de'ang lus kyis bsrung bar bya ba sku'i dam tshig la'ang phyi nang gsang ba gsum las /
NK105(be)002:19825: ma byin par len pa spong ba dang /
NK105(be)002:19826: phyi'i nang du mi tshangs par spyod pa spong ba dang /
NK105(be)002:19827: phyi'i gsang bar srog gcod pa spong ba ste /
NK105(be)002:19828: rdo rje snying po khang bu brtsegs pa'i rgyud las /
NK105(be)002:19829: sku yi phyi yi dam tshig la //
NK105(be)002:19830: rnam pa gsum du rab phye ste //
NK105(be)002:19831: ma byin blangs pas phyi yi yang //
NK105(be)002:19832: sku yi dam tshig nyams par 'gyur //
NK105(be)002:19833: de yi rtags su yan lag nad //
NK105(be)002:19834: mi bzad sna tshogs lus la 'byung //
NK105(be)002:19835: mi tshangs spyad pa nad yin te //
NK105(be)002:19836: rtags su dbang po'i nad rnams so //
NK105(be)002:19837: srog bcad pa ni gsang ba ste //
NK105(be)002:19838: de yi rtags su don snod nad //
NK105(be)002:19841: de dag bskang ba'i thabs kyang /
NK105(be)002:19842: dam tshig mchog gi rgyud las /
NK105(be)002:19843: rtags dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK105(be)002:19844: phyi yi phyi la lder chos dang //
NK105(be)002:19845: ri mo'i las ni lan bdun gyis //
NK105(be)002:19846: de yi sdig pa las grol ba'o //
NK105(be)002:19848: sngags phyi'i lha rnams kyi lder chos dang ri mo bdun byas pas skongs so //
NK105(be)002:19850: phyi yi nang la lugs sku bdun //
NK105(be)002:19851: rab tu gnas pa rtsol bas bzhengs //
NK105(be)002:19852: bla ma mchog la dbul bar bya //
NK105(be)002:19853: zhes pas sngags nang gi lha'i sku lugs ma bdun byas te bla ma la dbul lo //
NK105(be)002:19856: phyi yi gsang ba'i rtags byung na //
NK105(be)002:19857: rdo rje dang ni dril bu nyid //
NK105(be)002:19858: dagu'am bcu gcig bla ma la'o //
NK105(be)002:19860: sku'i nang gi phyi nang gsang ba gsum ni /
NK105(be)002:19861: gser gyi khang bu brtsegs pa'i rgyud las /
NK105(be)002:19862: nang gi phyi ni spun dang yang //
NK105(be)002:19863: gang gi pha dang ma nyid dang //
NK105(be)002:19864: rang gi lus la mi smad do //
NK105(be)002:19865: nang gi nang nyid spyir na yang //
NK105(be)002:19866: theg pa che chung chos rnams la //
NK105(be)002:19868: zhugs te gzugs brnyan 'dzin pa'i lus //
NK105(be)002:19869: smad cing mtho btsams rgyan smad na //
NK105(be)002:19870: sangs rgyas sku ni brgya phrag blus //
NK105(be)002:19871: nang gi gsang ba rang gi lus //
NK105(be)002:19872: lha yi dkyil 'khor yin pa'i phyir //
NK105(be)002:19873: sman dang zas la dug 'dres zos //
NK105(be)002:19874: gal te mtshon gyis btab na yang //
NK105(be)002:19875: zag pa'i lam med lus brgya blangs //
NK105(be)002:19876: de 'og tsha ba'i dmyal ba myong //
NK105(be)002:19878: de dag bskang ba yang 'gyod pas gshags par bya'o //
NK105(be)002:19880: dpal nyi zla brtsegs pa'i rgyud las /
NK105(be)002:19881: rdo rje spun nam sring mo yi //
NK105(be)002:19882: lus kyi rgyan la dpyas pa dang //
NK105(be)002:19883: mtho brtsams lag gis brdeg pa'i tshul //
NK105(be)002:19884: gal te gzhan gyis byed bcug na //
NK105(be)002:19886: nang gi shin tu 'dres pa'i mched //
NK105(be)002:19887: ku re rtsed mo'i tshul tsam du'ang //
NK105(be)002:19888: brdeg gam brdeg par brtsams pa'am //
NK105(be)002:19889: rmi lam na yang yum la gtses //
NK105(be)002:19890: de ma thag tu ma bshags na //
NK105(be)002:19891: 'di yang sngar dang sdig mnyam mo //
NK105(be)002:19892: gsang ba'i gsang ba bla ma yi //
NK105(be)002:19893: sku yi grib mar mi 'gong la //
NK105(be)002:19894: bla ma'i spyan lam dag tu yang //
NK105(be)002:19895: mtshon cha gzung bar mi bya'o //
NK105(be)002:19896: rkang lag brkyang dang nyal mi bya //
NK105(be)002:19897: skyil krung 'dug dang rgyab mi bstan //
NK105(be)002:19898: lham dang stan dang bzhon pa dang //
NK105(be)002:19899: gdugs sogs sgeg pa'i rgyan rnams spang //
NK105(be)002:19900: bla ma'i gzims khang dag la yang //
NK105(be)002:19901: lag pas mtshon nam rdo dag gis //
NK105(be)002:19902: btsam par bya ba ma yin no //
NK105(be)002:19904: bla ma'i gnas khang bshig pa dang //
NK105(be)002:19905: sku la btsams shing sdig byas pa //
NK105(be)002:19906: 'di yi sdig pa pha mtha' yas //
NK105(be)002:19907: gal te bla mar bag med pas //
NK105(be)002:19908: ma dpyad bsdongs na'ang pha mtha' yas //
NK105(be)002:19909: mchog tu sku la brnyas byas na //
NK105(be)002:19910: 'di yi rnam smin brjod mi lang //
NK105(be)002:19912: de'ang bla ma'i phyogs la brten pa'i sdig pa ni gzhan las 'bum 'gyur gyis lci bas /
NK105(be)002:19913: bzhugs na de nyid la nyin zhag gis bar ma chod par bshags /
NK105(be)002:19914: mi bzhugs kyang de'i sku 'bag la sogs pa'i drung du bshags so //
NK105(be)002:19915: gsung gi dam tshig kyang phyi nang gsang ba gsum gsum las /
NK105(be)002:19917: brdzun du smra ba spong ba ste /
NK105(be)002:19918: 'khor lo rnam par brtsegs pa'i rgyud las /
NK105(be)002:19919: sngags kyi mos pa spyod pa yis //
NK105(be)002:19920: 'gro ba phal pa dag la yang //
NK105(be)002:19921: brdzun pa'i tshig ni rang 'dod kyis //
NK105(be)002:19922: smra la rtag tu dga' ba la //
NK105(be)002:19923: sngags bzlas nus pa mi 'byung zhing //
NK105(be)002:19924: gzhan la smras pa btsun pa min //
NK105(be)002:19925: rang gi ngag nyid nyams pa yis //
NK105(be)002:19927: ma 'ongs dus na sme sha'i lus //
NK105(be)002:19928: byang gi phyogs su myong bar 'gyur //
NK105(be)002:19929: de 'og ngan sog sdug bsngal yang //
NK105(be)002:19930: rnam pa sna tshogs myong bar 'gyur //
NK105(be)002:19932: phyi'i nang du phra ma mi smra ba ste /
NK105(be)002:19934: sngags la zhugs pa'i gang zag gang //
NK105(be)002:19935: gzhan gnyis dbyer 'jug phra ma smra //
NK105(be)002:19937: ci byas log par 'gyur ba dang //
NK105(be)002:19938: ma dpyad pa rnams dgrar 'gyur dang //
NK105(be)002:19939: lus la mtshon gyis 'debs pa dang //
NK105(be)002:19940: shi 'phos nas ni sder can lus //
NK105(be)002:19941: de nas ngan song rim gyis myong //
NK105(be)002:19943: phyi'i gsang bar gzhan gyi zher 'debs pa'i tshig mi smra ba ste /
NK105(be)002:19945: rtag tu zhe gcod tshig smra ba //
NK105(be)002:19946: snga ma'i las dang phyi ma'i rtags //
NK105(be)002:19947: 'gro ba byams bral bshes kyang sdang //
NK105(be)002:19949: shi 'phos rab tu dregs pa'i lus //
NK105(be)002:19950: de nas ngan song gsum du 'khor //
NK105(be)002:19952: gsung gi nang gi gsum ni /
NK105(be)002:19953: chos smra ba la smad na phyi /
NK105(be)002:19954: sgrub pa la smad pa nang /
NK105(be)002:19955: bsgom pa la smad pa gsang ba ste /
NK105(be)002:19956: dam tshig rnam par bkod pa'i rgyud las /
NK105(be)002:19957: sngags pa sdom la gnas pa yis //
NK105(be)002:19958: chos smra rnams dang chos sgrub dang //
NK105(be)002:19959: chos ni bsgom pa'i gang zag la //
NK105(be)002:19960: sgro zhing skur ba btab pa dang //
NK105(be)002:19961: gshe zhing smod pa'i tshig smras na //
NK105(be)002:19962: gzhan gyi mos pa nyams pa dang //
NK105(be)002:19963: rang gi bdog pa nyams pa dang //
NK105(be)002:19964: rang gi chos rnams brjed ngas te //
NK105(be)002:19966: ngan song sdug bsngal tshad med myong //
NK105(be)002:19968: gsang ba'i phyi rdo rje'i spun sring smad cing gshe skur btab pa'o //
NK105(be)002:19969: nang ni bla ma'i phyag rgya dang nye 'khor sun 'byin pa'i tshig smra ba'o //
NK105(be)002:19970: gsang ba bla ma la smod pa ste /
NK105(be)002:19971: phyag rgya gnyis sbyor gyi rgyud las /
NK105(be)002:19972: rdo rje'i mched dang lcam dral la //
NK105(be)002:19973: tshig gis smras dang ngag bcag na //
NK105(be)002:19974: bskal pa brgya phrag bye bar ni //
NK105(be)002:19975: khyad par ngan song gsum po yi //
NK105(be)002:19976: sdug bsngal mi bzad drag po nyid //
NK105(be)002:19977: gang zag de yi myong bar 'gyur //
NK105(be)002:19978: snga mar byas dang da lta'i rtags //
NK105(be)002:19979: rim par myong bar 'gyur ba ni //
NK105(be)002:19980: snga mar byas pas tshe 'di la //
NK105(be)002:19981: bar nas tha mar myong ba la //
NK105(be)002:19982: yang snga tshe sdod la byas te //
NK105(be)002:19983: skyes ma thag tu myong bar 'gyur //
NK105(be)002:19984: 'di la byas pa'i las mtha' ni //
NK105(be)002:19985: tshe 'di'i zhabs la ngag gi las //
NK105(be)002:19987: glo bur dag tu smra rgyun 'gag /
NK105(be)002:19988: bla ma'i bu dang chung ma dang //
NK105(be)002:19989: gang dag nyer gnas dag kyang rung //
NK105(be)002:19990: bka' las 'das shing ngag bcag na //
NK105(be)002:19991: snga ma las ni nyis 'gyur ro //
NK105(be)002:19992: yang na bla ma'i bye brag gis //
NK105(be)002:19993: rtsa ba dang ni yan lag gi //
NK105(be)002:19994: ngag 'das ngag tu smras pa dang //
NK105(be)002:19995: sgro skur 'dod tshig smras byas na //
NK105(be)002:19996: snga ma las ni stong phrag 'gyur //
NK105(be)002:19997: rnam par smin pa mi bzad pa //
NK105(be)002:19998: rim pas bla ma'i khyad kyis yang //
NK105(be)002:19999: de ma thag tu myong bar 'gyur //
NK105(be)002:20001: thugs kyi dam tshig la'ang gsum las /
NK105(be)002:20002: dang po phyi'i phyi ni gnod sems spong ba ste /
NK105(be)002:20003: snying po'i don rnam par len pa'i rgyud las /
NK105(be)002:20004: gang dag sngags pa rdo rje 'dzin //
NK105(be)002:20005: sems can gzhan nam rang yang rung //
NK105(be)002:20006: gnod par bya ba'i las 'chang na //
NK105(be)002:20007: 'di ni shu ba can gyi lus //
NK105(be)002:20008: grang ba'i reg par ldan pa yi //
NK105(be)002:20009: lus ni stong phrag lnga blangs nas //
NK105(be)002:20010: grang ba'i dmyal bar nges par skye //
NK105(be)002:20012: nang du brnab sems dang gnod sems spong ba ste /
NK105(be)002:20013: gnam lcags me ltar 'bar ba'i rgyud las /
NK105(be)002:20014: gal te sems can phal pa la //
NK105(be)002:20015: yul gyur gnod pa'i sems skyes na //
NK105(be)002:20016: 'gro ba thun mong lus can ni //
NK105(be)002:20017: brgya phrag gsum gyi srog bcad pa //
NK105(be)002:20018: 'di yi sdig pa'i cha dang mnyam //
NK105(be)002:20019: gal te bstan pa'i rtags 'dzin pa'i //
NK105(be)002:20020: gzugs can rnams la log 'gyur ro //
NK105(be)002:20021: sngags la zhugs pas brgya phrag 'gyur //
NK105(be)002:20022: rdo rje'i spun sring bdun phrag go //
NK105(be)002:20023: brgyud pa'i bla ma brgya phrag go //
NK105(be)002:20026: gsang bar rang gzhan gyi grub mtha' la log lta skyes pa ste /
NK105(be)002:20028: rang ngam gzhan gyi grub mtha' yi //
NK105(be)002:20029: chos la smod pa log pa'i lam //
NK105(be)002:20030: rtsa ba'i dam tshig las 'das na //
NK105(be)002:20031: sa spyod me yi sdug bsngal la //
NK105(be)002:20032: yun ring bar du gnas par 'gyur //
NK105(be)002:20033: rang gi grub mthar log lta skyes //
NK105(be)002:20034: dmyal ba nyid las thar skabs med //
NK105(be)002:20036: thugs kyi nang gi gsum la /
NK105(be)002:20039: gsang ba lta ba log pa spong ba ste /
NK105(be)002:20040: shel gyi khang bu brtsegs pa'i rgyud las /
NK105(be)002:20041: lta dang sgom dang spyod pa log /'di ni lam log chen po ste //
NK105(be)002:20042: sems can kun gyi sdug bsngal gang //
NK105(be)002:20043: 'di yi sems la smin par nges //
NK105(be)002:20046: phyi lta sgom spyod pa yid la ma byas pa /
NK105(be)002:20047: nang yi dam gyi lha yid lam byas pa /
NK105(be)002:20048: gsang ba bla ma dang rdo rje'i spun sring yid la ma byas pa ste /
NK105(be)002:20050: su yi yid kyi las 'khyal te //
NK105(be)002:20051: yid la bya ba'i chos rnams la //
NK105(be)002:20052: yid la ma byas nyams pa dang //
NK105(be)002:20053: 'das dang zhig pa'i las kyi mtha' //
NK105(be)002:20054: mnar med sdug bsngal myong ba'o //
NK105(be)002:20056: 'di dag kyang rang rang gi cha nyams pa bskang zhing /
NK105(be)002:20058: rtsa ba'i dam tshig bstan zin to //
NK105(be)002:20059: gnyis pa yan lag gi dam tshig lnga tshan lnga las /
NK105(be)002:20060: dang po shes par bya ba'i dam tshig lnga ni /
NK105(be)002:20061: chos thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas pas /
NK105(be)002:20064: rnam shes lnga byang chub sems dpa' lnga /
NK105(be)002:20066: rtog tshogs lnga'i dkyil 'khor lngar shes par bya ste /
NK105(be)002:20068: dang po shes par bya ba'i dam tshig ni //
NK105(be)002:20069: phung po lnga dang 'byung ba rnam pa lnga //
NK105(be)002:20070: rnam shes dbang po yul la sogs pa rnams //
NK105(be)002:20071: lha dang dkyil 'khor rang bzhin shes par bya //
NK105(be)002:20072: zhes pa ltar kun byed las kyang bshad do //
NK105(be)002:20073: gnyis pa spyad par bya ba'i dam tshig lnga ni /
NK105(be)002:20074: dam tshig chen po ste thabs la mkhas pas gzhan don du 'gyur ba'i tshe /
NK105(be)002:20080: spyad par bya ba'i dam tshig rnam lnga ni //
NK105(be)002:20081: ta na ga na ma byin len pa dang //
NK105(be)002:20082: mi tshangs spyod dang brdzun du smra ba dang //
NK105(be)002:20083: rnam pa lnga ni thabs mkhas spyod byed pa //
NK105(be)002:20084: ma spyad nyams mthong rtog dang bcas nas spyod //
NK105(be)002:20087: byang chub sems dpa'i sde snod las kyang /
NK105(be)002:20088: thabs chen rnams dang ldan pa la //
NK105(be)002:20089: nyon mongs byang chub yan lag 'gyur //
NK105(be)002:20090: zhes bshad pa dang tshul mthun pas /
NK105(be)002:20091: rang don gyi 'khris med pas gzhan don du gnang ba'i skabs sngar bstan pa bzhin yin no //
NK105(be)002:20092: gsum pa dang du blang ba'i dam tshig lnga ni /
NK105(be)002:20097: sha chen gyi dngas ma lnga ste /
NK105(be)002:20099: dang du blang ba'i dam tshig rnam lnga ni //
NK105(be)002:20100: dri chen dri chu la sogs dam rdzas lnga //
NK105(be)002:20103: mkha' 'gro ma rdo rje gur las /
NK105(be)002:20104: mi bskyod bsten pa'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK105(be)002:20105: nad kun rnam par spong bar 'gyur //
NK105(be)002:20106: rtag pa yis ni mdangs chen 'gyur //
NK105(be)002:20107: rdo rje nyi ma rgas pa med //
NK105(be)002:20108: rdo rje chos ni bsten pa yis //
NK105(be)002:20109: bud med kun la longs spyod do //
NK105(be)002:20110: srog chags lus 'byung rdo rje dag /
NK105(be)002:20111: don yod rgyal po chen po ste //
NK105(be)002:20112: dpal ldan don kun grub pa dang //
NK105(be)002:20113: rnal 'byor pa des zhi bar gtong //
NK105(be)002:20114: mi bskyod btung ba'i sbyor ba yis //
NK105(be)002:20116: rtag pa yis ni khri ru brjod //
NK105(be)002:20117: rdo rje nyi mas bye bar te //
NK105(be)002:20118: tshe dpag med kyis grangs med tshe //
NK105(be)002:20119: nam mkha' ji srid rta bdun pas //
NK105(be)002:20120: dpag med rdo rje nyi ma gnyis //
NK105(be)002:20121: 'khor ba bsgrub pa'i rtsa ba ste //
